hadiths[218]{hadithnumber,text}:
5521,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do martaba Soor phoonkey janey ka darmiyani waqfa chaalis hoga.'' unhoney kaha : Abu-Hurera ! chaalis din? unhoney kaha : mujhey malum nahin, unhoney puchha : chaalis maah? unhoney farmaya : main nahin janta, unhoney kaha : chaalis saal? unhoney kaha : main nahin janta.'' phir Allah aasman se pani nazil farmaeyga to wo is tarah ji uthen gey jis tarah sabziyan ug aati hain.'' farmaya : '' insan ki eik haddi ke siwa baqi sara jism gal-sad jaeyga, wo reedh ki haddi ka aakhiri sira hai, aur roze-qiyamat tamam makhluq usi se dobara banai jaeygi.'' aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''insan ko mitti kha jaeygi, albatta reedh ki haddi ka aakhiri sira baqi reh jaeyga, usi se wo paida kiya gaya aur usi se dobara banaya jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5522,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Allah zamin ko mutthi mein le-ley ga aur aasmano ko apney daain haath mein lapet lega, phir farmaeyga : main badshah hun, zamin ke badshah kahan hain?'' muttafaq aleh."
5523,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Allah aasmano ko lapet lega , phir unhen apney daain haath mein pakad lega , phir farmaeyga : main badshah hun, Jabir aur mutakabbir kahan hain? phir wo zaminon ko apney baaein hath mein lapet lega , eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''unko apney doosrey haath mein le-ley ga, phir farmaeyga , main badshah hun, Jabir aur mutakabbir kahan hain?'' rawahu Muslim."
5524,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Yahudi aalim Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to usney kaha : Muhammad ! roze-qiyamat Allah aasmano ko eik ungli par rok lega , zaminon ko eik ungli par , pahadon aur darakhton ko eik ungli par , pani aur mitti ko eik ungli par , aur baqi sari makhluq ko eik ungli par rok lega , phir unhen bulaeyga aur farmaeyga , main badshah hun, main Allah hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is baat par tajjub kartey huey aur uski tasdeeq kartey huey hans diye , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''unhoney Allah ki qadr na ki jis tarah uski qadr karney ka haq tha, aur roze-qiyamat tamam zamin uski mutthi mein hogi aur aasman uskey daain haath mein liptey huey hongey, paak hai wo zaat aur buland hai us se jo wo shirk kartey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5525,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Allah Taala ke us farman : ''us roz zamin ko dusri zamin se badal diya jaeyga.'' ke mutalliq puchha ke us roz log kahan hongey? farmaya : ''pul par.'' rawahu Muslim."
5526,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Suraj aur chaand ko lapet diya jaeyga.'' Bukhari."
5527,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main kaisey khush reh sakta hun jabkey Soor (phoonkney) waley ne us (Soor) ko apney munh ke sath laga rakha hai, apney kaan aur apni peshani ko jhuka rakha hai aur wo intizar kar raha hai ke usey phunk maarney ka kab hukm milta hai.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap hamein kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaho : hamarey liye Allah kafi hai aur wo behtareen karsaz hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5528,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Soor eik seeng hai jis mein phunk maari jaeygi.'' (sahih sanad) rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
5529,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah Taala ke farman (فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِیْ النَّاقُوْرِ) ki tafseer mein farmaya : (الرَّاجِفَۃُ) se pehli baar Soor phunka jana jabkey (الرَّادِفَۃُ) se dusri baar Soor phunka jana murad hai. Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne isey (ترجمۃ الباب) mein riwayat kiya hai.
5530,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Soor waley (Israafeel (Alaihissalam)) ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : ''uskey daain Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aur uskey baain Mekael (Alaihissalam) hongey.'' (rawahuRizeen)"
5531,"Hazrat Abu Rizeen Aqeeli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah makhluq ko dobara kaisey paida farmaeyga . aur uski makhluq mein kon si nishani (mojud) hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum kabhi apni qom ki khushk aur sakht wadi se guzrey ho? phir tum wahan se guzartey ho to wo sarsabz aur shadab lahlaha rahi hoti hai.'' maine arz kiya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo Allah ki uski makhluq mein nishani hai, Allah isi tarah mardon ko zinda kerega.'' dono hadise Rizeen ne naqal ki hain. rawahu Rizeen ."
5532,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon ko roze-qiyamat safed surkhi maael zamin par jama kiya jaeyga, wo (zameen) maide ki roti ki tarah hogi is mein kisi ke liye koi nishan nahin hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5533,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat zamin eik roti ki tarah hogi jisey Allah Taala ehale-jannat ki mezbani ke liye apney haath se is tarah ultey paltega jis tarah tum mein se koi dorane-safar apni roti ulat-palat karta hai.'' itney main eik Yahudi aaya aur usney kaha : Abu Qasim! Rehman aap par barkat nazil farmaai , kya main aap ko roze-qiyamat ehle-jannat ki mezbani ke mutalliq na bataaun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zarur bataao.'' usney kaha : zamin eik roti ki tarah hogi jis tarah Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya , phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamari taraf dekha aur hansney lagey yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagin, phir us (yahudi) ne kaha : kya main aap ko unke salan ke mutalliq na bataaun? (us ne khud hi bataya) بالام aur noon, Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye kya chiz hai? usney kaha : bail aur machli, un dono ki kaleji ke sath , gosht ka tukda jo ke alehda latak raha hota hai, uskey sath sattar-hazar afrad khaeyngey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5534,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log teen firqon mein jama kiye jaeyngey, raghbat karney aur darney waley eik oont par do (sawar) hongey, eik oont par teen hongey, eik oont par chaar hongey aur eik oont par das hongey, jabkey baqi logon ko aag jama karegi, jab wo qailula karengey to wo unke sath qailula karegi, jab wo raat guzaareingey to wo bhi unke sath raat guzaareygi, jahan wo subah karengey wo subah karegi aur jahan wo Sham karengey wo (shaam ke waqt) unke sath Sham karegi.'' muttafaq aleh."
5535,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum nangey paaon , nangey badan aur be-khatna uthaey jaaogey.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaaee : ''jaisa ke ham ne paida kiya tha pehli martaba ham aisey hi lautaaein jaeyngey, ye hamari taraf se eik wada hai jisey ham pura karkey rahengey.'' aur roze-qiyamat sab se pehley Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko libas pehnaya jaeyga, aur merey as-haab se baaz ko jahannam mein ley janey ke liye pakda jaeyga to main kahunga : ye merey as-haab hain, ye merey as-haab hain ! to wo kahega : aap ke baad ye log apni edhiyon ke bal phir gaey they, to main bhi wohi kahunga jo nek bandey Esa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha tha : ''jab tak main un mein tha to main un par nigraan tha. . . . . العزیز الحکیم.'' tak. muttafaq aleh."
5536,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''log roze-qiyamat nangey paaon , nangey badan aur bila khatna uthaey jaeyngey.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mard aur aurten ikhattey hongey, wo eik doosrey ko dekhengey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aaisha ! wo (qiyamat ka ( maamla us se bahut sangeen hoga ke wo eik doosrey ko dekhen.'' muttafaq aleh."
5537,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi ! kafir ko roze-qiyamat uskey chehrey ke bal kaisey chalaya jaeyga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wo zaat jisney usey duniya mein paaon par chalaya is par qadir nahin ke wo roze-qiyamat usey uskey chehrey ke bal chalaey?'' muttafaq aleh."
5538,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) roze-qiyamat apney walid Aazar se milengey to Aazar ke chehrey par siyahi aur ghubar hoga, Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) usey farmaeyngey : kya maine tumhen nahin kaha tha ke meri mukhalifat na karo, unka walid un se kahega : aaj main tumhari mukhalifat aur nafarmani nahin karta , Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) arz karengey : rab ji ! to ne mujh se wada kiya tha ke to roze-qiyamat mujhey ruswa nahin kerega? is se ziyada ruswai kya hai ke mera walid (teri rehmat sey) sab se ziyada door hai? is par Allah Taala farmaeyga : maine jannat kafiron par haram kar di hai, phir Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) se kaha jaeyga : tumharey qadmon taley kya hai? wo dekhengey to wahan (Aazar ki bajaey) eik ghaney baalon wala bijju hoga, jo apni ghilazat ke sath lat-pat hoga, usko uskey paaon se pakad kar jahannam mein dal diya jaeyga.'' Bukhari."
5539,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat log paseeney mein sharobor hongey yahan tak ke unka paseena zamin par sattar haath tak phel jaeyga, aur wo unke munh tak hota hua unke kanon tak pahunch jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5540,"Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''roze-qiyamat Suraj makhluq ke qarib ho jaeyga yahan tak ke wo meel ki masafat ke barabar unke qarib hoga, aur log apney aamaal ke mutabiq paseeney mein (doobey) hongey, un mein se kisi ke takhnon tak hoga, kisi ke ghutnon tak hoga, kisi ke izaar baandhney ki jagah tak aur baaz ke munh tak hoga.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath se apney munh ki taraf ishara kiya. rawahu Muslim."
5541,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmaeyga : aey Adam ! wo arz karengey : hazir hun, tayyar hun, aur sari khair terey haathon mein hai. wo farmaeyga : jahannam janey walon ko nikal do , wo arz karengey , jahannam janey waley kitney hain? wo farmaeyga : her hazar mein se no-sau-ninnanwey, us waqt bachchey boodhey ho jaeyngey, her hamal wali apna hamal gira deygi, aur tum logon ko madhoshi ke aalim mein dekhogey , halanke wo madhosh nahin hongey, balke Allah ka azab shadeed hoga .''Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein se wo eik kon hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen basharat ho, kyonkey wo eik aadmi tum mein se hoga jabkey yajooj Majuj hazar hongey.'' phir farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! mujhey ummid hai ke eik chothai jannati tum hogey.'' ham ne (khush ho kar) naare takbir buland kiya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ummid karta hun ke tum jannat main eik tihai hogey.'' ham ne phir naarae takbir buland kiya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ummid karta hun ke nisf (aadhe) jannati tum hogey.'' ham ne Allahu-Akbar kaha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum tamam logon mein itney hogey jitney safed bail ki jild par eik siyah baal, ya kisi siyah bail ki jild par eik safed baal hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5542,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''hamara rab (roze-qiyamat) apni pindli zahir karega to her momin mard aur momina aurat uskey liye sajda rez ho jaeyngey, sirf wohi baqi reh jaeyga jo duniya mein riya aur shohrat ki khatir sajda kiya karta tha, wo sajda karna chaheyga lekin uski kamar takhta bin jaeygi  aur wo sajde ke liye jhuk nahin sakeygi).'' muttafaq aleh."
5543,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat eik mota taza shakhs aaeyga , Allah ke yahan wo machar ke par ke barabar bhi nahin hoga.'' aur farmaya : ''ye aayat padho : roze-qiyamat ham unka koi wazan nahin karengey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5544,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''jis roz wo (zameen) apni khabren bata dey gi.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho uski khabren kya hain?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uski khabren ye hain ke wo her mard aur her aurat ke mutalliq uskey tamam aamaal ke mutalliq gawahi degi jo usney uski pusht par kiye hongey, wo kaheygi : usney falan falan din mujh par falan falan kaam kiya tha.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye uski khabren hain.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5545,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bhi faut hota hai to wo hasrat aur afsos karta hai.'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! uski hasrat aur afsos kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo neku-kaar tha to wo afsos karta hai ke usney ziyada nekiyan kyon nahin kin, aur agar wo gunah gaar tha to wo afsos karta hai ke usney gunah kyon na chodey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5546,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat logon ko teen iqsaam (hisson) mein jama kiya jaeyga, eik qism pedal chalney walon ki hogi , eik sawaron ki aur eik giroh apney chehron ke bal chal raha hoga .'' arz kiya gaya Allah ke Rasool ! wo apney chehron ke bal kaisey chalen gey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis zaat ne unhen unke qadmon par chalaya wo is par qadir hai ke wo unhen chehron ke bal chala dey, suno ! wo (kuffar) her oonchi jagah aur kaantay (her takleef deh chiz) se apney chehron ke zariey apna bachaaw karengey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5547,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs roze-qiyamat ka aakhon dekha manzar dekhna pasand karta ho to wo Sura التکویر الانفطار aur Sura الانشقاق ki tilawat karey.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5548,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sachche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hadees bayan ki ke ''logon ko teen girohon mein jama kiya jaeyga, eik giroh ke log sawaariyon par hongey, khatey peetey aur khush haal hongey, eik giroh aisa hoga ke farishtey unhen unke chehron ke bal ghaseet rahey hon gey , aur wo unhen (jahannam ki) aag mein jama karengey , aur eik giroh hoga ke wo chal rahey hongey aur daud rahey hongey, aur Allah sawaariyon par koi aafat bhejeyga to koi sawari baqi nahin rahegi, yahan tak ke aadmi ka baagh hoga wo usey sawari ke badley mein dega lekin wo is par qadir nahin hoga.'' rawahu Nasai."
5549,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat jis kisi se hisab liya gaya wo maara gaya.'' maine arz kiya, kya Allah ne ye nahin farmaya : ''(jis kisi ko namae-aamaal uskey daain haath mein diya jaeyga) us se aasan hisab liya jaeyga.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to sirf pesh karna hoga, lekin jiski hisab mein janch padtaal ki gaee wo halak hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5550,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se her eik ke sath uska rab kalam farmaeyga , uskey aur us (bandey) ke darmiyan koi tarjamaan hoga na koi hijaab hoga jo usey chupa sakey , apney daain dekhega to wo apney aamaal hi dekhega jo usney aagey bhejey they, wo apney baain dekhega to wo aagey bhejey huey apney aamaal hi dekhega , wo apney aagey chehrey ke samney dekhega to usey (jahannam) ki aag hi nazar aaeygi , tum (jahannam ki) aag se bacho chahey (chaahe) khajoor ke eik tukdey hi ke zariey ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
5551,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah momin ko qarib kar lega , is par apna parda dal dega aur usey chhupa kar farmaeyga : kya tum falan gunah pehchantey ho? kya tum ko falan gunah yad hai? wo arz kerega, rab ji ! ji haan , yahan tak ke jab wo usey uskey gunahon ka aetraaf aur iqrar kara lega to wo shakhs apney dil mein socheyga ke wo to maara gaya, Allah Taala farmaeyga : maine duniya mein terey gunahon par parda daley rakha aur aaj mein terey gunah maaf karta hun, usey uski nekiyon ki kitab (aamaal nama) de-di jaeygi, albatta kuffar aur munafiq to unhen sari makhluq ke samney bulaya jaeyga aur kaha jaeyga : ''ye wo log hain jinhonne apney rab par jhoot baandha tha, sun lo ! zalimon par Allah ki lanat ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
5552,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab qiyamat ka din hoga to Allah her musalman ko eik Yahudi ya eik Esai dega aur farmaeyga : iskey badley mein (jahannam ki) aag se teri azadi hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5553,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Nuh (Alaihissalam) ko laya jaeyga to un se kaha jaeyga : kya aapney (Allah taala ke ehkamaat aur ta'leemaat) pahuncha diye they? wo kahengey : ji haan , merey parwardigar ! unki ummat se puchha jaeyga : kya unhoney tumhen Allah Taala ke ehkamaat pahuncha diye they? wo kahengey : hamarey paas to koi daraney (aagah karney) wala aaya hi nahin. un se kaha jaeyga : aap ka gawah kon hai? wo kahengey : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur unki ummat.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir tumhen laya jaeyga, to tum gawahi dogey ke unhoney pahuncha diya tha.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''ham ne isi tarah tumhen beech ki ummat  banaya ta ke tum logon par gawah ho aur Rasulullah tum par gawah hon.'' Bukhari."
5554,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas they to aap hans diye , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke main kis wajeh se hans raha hun?'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, farmaya : bandey ke apney rab se mukhatib honey sey, wo arz karega : rab ji ! kya aap mujhey zulm se nahin bachaeyn gey?'' farmaya : ''wo (Rab taalaa) farmaeyga : kyon nahin, zarur.'' farmaya : ''wo arz kerega : main apney khilaf sirf apney nafs hi ki gawahi qubul karunga , farmaya : ''Allah taala farmaeyga : ''aaj tera nafs hi terey khilaf gawahi deney ke liye kafi hai. aur likhney waley moazziz farishtey bhi gawahi ke liye kafi hain.'' farmaya : ''iskey munh par mohar laga di jaeygi, aur uskey aaza se kaha jaeyga, kalam karo.'' farmaya : ''wo uskey aamaal ke mutalliq bolengey, phir us (bandey) ke aur uski zaban ke darmiyan se pabandi utha li jaeygi.'' farmaya : ''wo (apni zaban se bol kar) kahega : tumharey liye doori ho aur halakat ho, main to tumhari hi taraf se jhagda tha.'' rawahu Muslim."
5555,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sahaba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham roze-qiyamat apney rab ko dekhen gey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum , do-pehar ke waqt jabkey aasman mein baadal na ho, Suraj dekhney mein koi takleef mehsus kartey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : nahin ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum , chaudahwin raat jabkey aasman mein baadal bhi na ho, chaand dekhney mein koi takleef mehsus kartey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : nahin ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum apney rab ke deedar mein bas itni takleef mehsus karogey, jis tarah tum un dono (Suraj aur chaand) mein se kisi eik ko dekhney mein takleef mehsus kartey ho.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala bandey se mulaqat kerega to wo farmaeyga : aey falan ! kya maine tumhen izzat nahin bakhshi thi? kya maine tumhen sardar nahin banaya tha? kya maine tujhey biwi nahin di thi? kya maine ghodey aur oont terey liye musakhkhar (paida) nahin kiye they? kya maine tujhey (teri qom par) sardar nahin banaya tha? aur to un se chotha hissey wasul karta tha? wo kahega : kyon nahin.'' farmaya : ''rab taala farmaeyga : kya to janta tha ke to mujh se mulaqat karney wala hai? wo kahega : nahin, phir rab taala farmaeyga : maine (aaj) tujhey bhula diya jis tarah tum ne mujhey (duniya mein) bhula rakha tha, phir rab taala doosrey se mulaqat karega , aur usi (pehley) ke jaise zikr kiya, phir wo teesrey se mulaqat kerega to wo us se bhi usi ki jase kahega : wo arz kerega : rab ji ! main aap par , aap ki kitab par aur aap ke Rasulon par eman laya , maine Namaz padhi , roza rakha , sadqa kiya, aur wo jis qadr ho saka apni tareef kerega, rab taala farmaeyga : yahin thehrao , phir kaha jaeyga : ham abhi tujh par gawah pesh kartey hain, wo apney dil mein ghor aur fikr kerega, wo kon hai jo merey khilaf gawahi dega , uskey munh par mohar laga di jaeygi, aur uski raan se kaha jaeyga, bolo , chunanche uski raan , uska gosht aur uski haddiyan uskey amal ke mutabiq kalam kerengi , aur ye isliye hoga ta ke Allah Taala uskey nafs ki taraf se uska uzr zaayel (khatm) kar dey , aur ye munafiq shakhs hoga, aur ye wo hoga jis par Allah naraz hoga.'' rawahu Muslim. aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (یدخل من امتی الجنۃ) ba-riwaayat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , (baabul tawakul) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
5556,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''merey rab ne merey sath wada kiya hai ke wo meri ummat se sattar hazar afrad hisab aur azab ke baghair jannat mein ley jaeyga. aur her hazar ke sath sattar hazar hongey. aur mazeed ye ke merey rab ki taraf se teen chullu hongey.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
5557,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat log teen baar (Allah ke huzur) pesh kiye jaeyngey, pehli do martaba ki peshi mein jhagda aur mazrat hogi aur teesri peshi ke waqt haathon ki taraf aamaal namey udengey, chunanche koi unhen apney daain haath mein pakadney wala hoga aur koi baain mein.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees is wajeh se sahih nahin ke Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se nahin suna. rawahu Ahmed."
5558,Aur baaz raawiyon ne isey Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) ke wastey se Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja aur Ahmed.
5559,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Allah meri ummat ke eik aadmi ko sari makhluq ke samney layega aur uskey ninnanwey rajister kholeyga , aur her rajister ki lambaai hade-nazar tak hogi , phir Allah Taala farmaeyga : kya tum in mein se kisi chiz ka inkar kartey ho (ke tum ne na ki ho)? ya merey likhney walon ne , hifazat karney walon ne tum par koi zulm kiya ho? wo arz kerega, rab ji ! nahin, Allah farmaeyga : kya terey paas koi uzr hai? wo arz kerega : rab ji ? nahin, Allah farmaeyga : haan hamarey paas teri eik neki hai, kyonkey aaj tum par koi zulm nahin hoga, eik kard nikala jaeyga, is par darj hoga : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. Allah farmaeyga : wazan par hazir ho, wo arz kerega : rab ji ! un rajistaron ke muqabley mein is kard ki kya haisiyat hai? chunanche Allah wo farmaeyga : aaj tum par koi zulm nahin kiya jaeyga, farmaya : eik paldey mein wo dafaatir rakhey jaeyngey aur doosrey paldey mein wo kard rakha jaeyga to wo dafaatir halkay pad jaeyngey aur wo kard bhari ho jaeyga, Allah ke naam ke muqabley mein koi chiz bhari nahin ho sakti.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
5560,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney jahannam ki aag ko yad kiya to wo ro padin , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen kon si chiz rulaa rahi hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, maine jahannam ki aag ko yad kiya to main ro padi, to kya roze-qiyamat aap apney ehlae-khana ko yad rakhengey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! teen maqamat hain, jahan koi kisi ko yad nahin kerega, meezaan (tarazu) ke moqe par yahan tak ke wo jaan ley ke aaya uski meezaan halki padti hai ya wo bhari hoti hai, namae-aamaal ke waqt , jab kaha jaeyga : ''aao apna namae-aamaal padho.'' yahan tak ke wo jaan ley ke uska namae-aamaal kahan diya jata hai, uskey daain haath mein ya uski pusht ke peechhey se uskey baaein hath mein milta hai, aur pul-siraat ke moqe par jab usey jahannam par rakha jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5561,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik aadmi aaya aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney beth gaya to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! merey kuchh ghulam hain, wo merey sath jhoot boltey hain, khayanat kartey hain, aur meri nafarmani kartey hain, jabkey main unhen bura bhala kehta hun aur unhen maarta hun, unki wajeh se (Allah taala ke yahan) mera maamla kaisa hoga? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab roze-qiyamat hoga to unhoney tujh se jo khayanat ki hogi , teri nafarmani ki hogi aur tujh se jhoot bola hoga unka aur to ne jo unhen saza di hogi uska hisab kiya jaeyga, agar teri saza unki ghaltiyon ke mutabiq hui to phir maamla barabar rahega terey liye koi sawab aur azaab nahin hoga aur agar teri saza unki khataaon se kam rahi to phir tujhey zayed haq hasil hoga aur agar teri saza unke gunahon se ziyada hui to phir uski ziyadti ka tujh se unhen badla dilaaya jaeyga.'' (ye sun kar) wo aadmi (majlis sey) door ho kar cheekhney aur roney laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''kya tum Allah ka farman nahin padhtey : ''ham roze-qiyamat insaf ka tarazu qaaim karengey to kisi jaan par koi zulm nahin kiya jaeyga, agar (amal aur zulm) raai ke daney ke barabar bhi ho, to ham usey ley aaeyngey aur kafi hain ham hisab karney waley.'' chunanche us aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main apney liye aur unke liye , unki alehdgi se behtar koi chiz nahin paata, main aap ko gawah banata hun ke wo sarey azad hain. rawahu Tirmizi."
5562,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko unki kisi Namaz mein ye dua (اَللّٰھُمَّ حَاسِبْنِیْ حِسَابًا یَّسِیْرًا) ''aey Allah ! mera aasan hisab lena.'' kartey huey suna to maine arz kiya, Allah ke Nabi ! aasan hisab se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(us se murad ye hai ke) (Allah Taalaa) uskey namae-aamaal par nazar dal kar us se darguzar farmaeyga , kyonkey Aaisha ! us roz jiskey hisab ki janch parrtaal ki gaee to wo maara gaya.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5563,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye to unhoney arz kiya : mujhey bataeyn ke Shan Wale Allah ne jo ye farmaya hai : ''us din log Rabbul-Aalemeen ke huzur khadey hongey.'' to roze-qiyamat khadey honey ki kon taqat rakhega? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(qiyamat ka din) momin par halka kar diya jaeyga yahan tak ke wo is par farz Namaz ki tarah hoga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi al-ba's aur Nushur).
5564,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us din ke mutalliq puchha gaya jiski miqdaar pachas hazar saal hogi ke us din ki tawaalat (lambai) kis qadr hogi (kya log itna lamba qiyam kar sakengey)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! us (din) ko momin par is qadr aasan kar diya jaeyga ke wo is par farz Namaz se bhi halka ho jaeyga jo usney duniya mein padhi thi.'' dono hadise ko Imam Behaqi ne '' kitab al-ba's aur Nushur'' main naqal kiya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi al-ba's aur Nushur)."
5565,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat tamam logon ko eik jagah par jama kiya jaeyga to aelan karney wala aelan kerega : wo tahajjud guzar kahan hain? wo khadey hongey aur wo qaleel (kam) hongey, aur wo baghair hisab jannat mein jaeyngey, phir baqi logon ke hisab ke mutalliq hukm farmaya jaeyga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5566,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (Mairaj ki raat) main jannat mein chal raha tha ke achcha main eik nehar par pahuncha , uskey dono kinaron par khaul daar motiyon ke gumbad they, maine kaha : Jibrael ! ye kya hai? unhoney kaha : ye kausar hai, jo aap ke rab ne aap ko ata farmaee hai, maine dekha ke uski mitti aa'laa khushbu wali kastoori thi.'' Bukhari."
5567,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera hoz eik maah ki masafat (doori) ke barabar hai, uskey atraaf barabar hain. uska pani doodh se ziyada safed hai, uski khushbu kastoori se ziyada achchhi hai aur uskey piyaley aasman ke sitaron ki tarah hain, jis shakhs ne us se pi liya wo phir kabhi (maidane-hashr mein) piyasa na hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5568,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera hoz ila aur adn ke darmiyani masafat (doori) se ziyada masafat (doori) wala hai. wo barf se ziyada safed , aur wo shehad miley doodh se ziyada sheereen (meetha) aur lazeez hai, uskey bartan sitaron ki tadaad se ziyada hain, aur main (doosrey) logon ko us se is tarah door hataunga jis tarah aadmi logon ke oonton ko apney hoz se door hataataa hai.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap us roz hamein pehchan lengey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, tumharey liye eik khas nishan hoga jo kisi aur ummat ke liye nahin hoga. tum merey paas us haalat mein aao gey ke wuzu ke nishan ki wajeh se tumhari peshani aur haath paaon chamaktey hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5569,"Aur Sahih Muslim ki Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''us (hoz) mein soney aur chaandi ke piyaley aasman ke sitaron ki tarah hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5570,"Aur Sahih Muslim hi ki eik hadees , jo ke Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, is mein hai : aap se uskey mashrub (sharbat) ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo doodh se ziyada safed aur shehad se ziyada mitha hai, is mein jannat se do parnaaley girtey hain, un mein se eik soney ka hai jabkey doosra chaandi ka.'' rawahu Muslim."
5571,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main hoz par tum se pehley hi mojud hunga jo shakhs merey paas se guzreyga, wo (us sey) piyega aur jisney pi liya usey kabhi piyas nahin lageygi, kuchh log merey paas aaeyngey , main unhen pehchanta hunga aur wo mujhey pehchantey hongey, phir merey aur unke darmiyan rukawat khadi kar di jaeygi, main kahunga : ye to mujh se hain, (merey ummati hain), mujhey kaha jaeyga : aap nahin jantey ke unhoney aap ke baad Deen mein kya kiya naey kaam ejaad kar liye they, mein kahunga is shakhs ke liye (mujh sey) doori ho jisney merey baad Deen mein tabdili kar li.'' muttafaq aleh."
5572,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mominon ko roze-qiyamat roke rakha jaeyga yahan tak ke us wajeh se wo ghamgin ho jaeyngey, wo kahengey : kaash! ke ham apney rab ke huzur koi sifarishi talash karen ta ke wo hamein hamari us jagah se najat dey dey , wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey , aur kahengey : aap Adam , tamam insanon ke baap hain, Allah Taala ne aap ko apney haath se takhleeq farmaya (banaya), aap ko jannat mein basaya , apney farishton se aap ko sajda karaya aur aap ko tamam chizon ke naam sikhaey , apney rab ke huzur hamari sifarish karen yahan tak ke wo hamein hamari us jagah se najat dey dey , wo kahengey : main wahan tumhari sifarish nahin kar sakta , wo apni us khata ko yad karengey jis ka irtikab us darkht ke khaney se hua tha halanke unhen us se mana kiya gaya tha, balke tum Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao , wo pehley Nabi hain, jinhen Allah Taala ne eahle zamin ki taraf Nabi banakar bheja tha, wo Nuh (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey to wo bhi yehi kahengey , main wahan tumhari sifarish nahin kar sakta , aur wo apni us khata ko yad karengey jo un se la-ilmi mein apney rab se sawal karney se sarzad hui thi, balke tum Rehman ke khaleel Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao.'' farmaya : ''wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaeyngey, to wo bhi yehi kahengey : main wahan tumhari sifarish nahin kar sakta , aur wo apney teen jhooton ko yad karengey jo unhoney boley they, balke tum Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao jo Allah ke aisey bandey hain jinhen Allah Taala ne Torat ata ki, un se kalam farmaya aur sargoshi ke liye unhen qarib kiya.'' farmaya : ''wo Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaeyngey to wo bhi kahengey mein wahan tumhari sifarish nahin kar sakta , aur wo apni us ghalati ka tazkira karengey ke unhoney us (qibti) aadmi ko qatl kiya tha, balke tum Allah ke bandey Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao jo ke uskey Rasool hain, Allah ki rooh aur uska kalma hain.'' farmaya : '' wo Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaeyngey to wo bhi yehi kahengey , main wahan tumhari sifarish nahin kar sakta , balke tum Allah ke bandey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaao , Allah ne jinkey agley pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye hain.'' farmaya : ''chunanche wo merey paas aaeyngey main apney rab sey, uskey huzur aaney ki, ijazat talab karunga to mujhey ijazat de-di jaeygi, jab main Allah Taala ko dekhunga to sajda rez ho jaaunga, phir jitni der Allah chaheyga wo mujhey usi haalat mein rehney dega, phir farmaeyga : Muhammad ! utho , baat karo, tumhari baat suni jaeygi, sifarish karo, tumhari sifarish qubul ki jaeygi, aap sawal karen, aap ko ata kiya jaeyga.'' farmaya : ''chunanche main apna sar uthaaunga to main apney rab ki wo hamd aur sanaa bayan karunga , jo wo mujhey sikhaeyga , phir main sifarish karunga to merey liye tadaad ka ta'yun kar diya jaeyga, main (darbare-Ilaahi sey) bahar aaunga aur main unhen jahannam ki aag se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil kar dunga, phir main dusri martaba jaaunga, aur apney rab ke huzur pesh honey ki ijazat talab karunga, mujhey uskey paas janey ki ijazat mil jaeygi, jab main usey dekhunga to sajda rez ho jaaun ga, jis qadr Allah chaheyga wo mujhey usi haalat mein rehney dega, phir farmaeyga : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sar uthaao, baat karo, tumhen suna jaeyga, sifarish karo tumhari sifarish qubul ki jaeygi, sawal karo aap ko ata kiya jaeyga.'' farmaya : ''main apna sar uthaunga, mein apney rab ki hamd aur sanaa bayan karunga jo wo mujhey sikhaeyga, phir main sifarish karunga to merey liye had mutayyan kar di jaeygi, main (baargaahe Rabbul-Izzat sey) bahar aaunga to main unhen jahannam se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil kar dunga, phir main teesri martaba jaaunga, apney rab ke paas janey ki ijazat talab karunga to mujhey uskey paas janey ki ijazat mil jaeygi, jab main usey dekhunga to sajdey mein gir jaaunga , Allah jab tak chaheyga mujhey usi haalat mein chhod dega phir farmaeyga : Muhammad ! sar uthaeyn , baat karen, tumhen suna jaeyga, sifarish karen tumhari sifarish qubul ki jaeygi, aur sawal karen aap ko ata kiya jaeyga.'' farmaya : ''main apna sar uthaunga aur apney rab ki hamd aur sanaa bayan karunga jo wo mujhey sikhaeyga, phir main sifarish karunga to merey liye had ka ta'yun kar diya jaeyga, main (baargaahe-Ilahi sey) bahar aaunga, unhen main aag se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil karunga , yahan tak ke jahannam mein sirf wohi reh jaeyga jisey Quran ne roke rakha hoga.'' yani jis par daaimi jahannami hona wajib ho chuka ho, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai.'' qarib hai ke aap ka rab aap ko maqame Mehmood par mab-us farmaai (bheje).'' farmaya : ''aur ye wo maqame Mehmood hai jis ka usney tumharey Nabi se wada farmaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5573,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab qiyamat ka din hoga to log iztirab ka shikar hongey wo mil kar Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey aur kahengey : apney rab se sifarish karo, wo kahengey : main uska ehal nahin hun, lekin tum Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao kyonkey wo Allah ke khaleel hain, wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaeyngey, wo bhi kahengey , main iska eahl nahin hun, lekin tum Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao kyonkey wo kaleemullah hain, wo Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey , wo bhi yehi kahengey : main iska ehal nahin hun, lekin tum Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao , kyonkey wo Allah ki rooh aur uska kalma hain, wo Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey , wo kahengey : main iska ehal nahin hun, lekin tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaao , chunanche wo merey paas aaeyngey to main kahunga : main iskey liye tayyar hun, main apney rab se ijazat talab karunga to mujhey ijazat de-di jaeygi, wo mujhey hamd ke alfaz ilhaam farmaeyga to main un (kalmiaat aur alfaz) ke zariey uski hamd bayan karunga, un kalimaat ka is waqt mujhey ilm nahin, main un hamdiya alfaz ke sath uski hamd bayan karunga aur uskey samney sajda rez ho jaaunga, mujhey kaha jaeyga, sawal karen aap ko ata kiya jaeyga aur sifarish karen aap ki sifarish qubul ki jaeygi, main kahunga : rab ji ! meri ummat , meri ummat ! chunanche kaha jaeyga jaao aur jiskey dil mein jau ke daney ke barabar eman hai usey (dozakh sey) nikal lo , main jaaunga aur aisey hi karunga , phir main dobara (rab ke huzur) jaaunga aur unhi hamdiya kalimaat ke zariey uski hamd bayan karunga , phir uskey huzur sajda rez ho jaaunga to kaha jaeyga, Muhammad ! apna sar uthaao, baat karo, suni jaeygi, sawal karo usey pura kiya jaeyga aur sifarish qubul ki jaeygi, main kahunga , rab ji ! meri ummat , meri ummat ! kaha jaeyga : jaao ! jiskey dil mein zarra ya raai ke daney ke barabar bhi eman hai usey (jahannam sey) nikal lo, main jaaunga aur aisey hi karunga , phir main (teesri martaba) lautoonga, aur un hamdiya kalimaat ke zariey uski hamd bayan karunga, phir uskey huzur sajda rez ho jaaunga, to kaha jaeyga : Muhammad ! apna sar uthaeyn , baat karen, suni jaeygi, sawal karen usey pura kiya jaeyga aur sifarish karen usey qubul kiya jaeyga, main kahunga : rab ji ! meri ummat , meri ummat ! kaha jaeyga : jaao aur jiskey dil mein raai ke daney se bhi adnaa tareen eman hai usey bhi jahannam ki aag se nikal lo, main jaaunga aur aisey hi karunga , phir main chauthi martaba lautoonga, aur un hamdiya kalimaat ke zariey uski hamd bayan karunga , phir uskey huzur sajda rez ho jaaunga to kaha jaeyga : Muhammad ! apna sar uthaeyn , baat karen suni jaeygi, maangen ata kiya jaeyga, aur sifarish karen tumhari sifarish qubul ki jaeygi, main kahunga : rab ji ! mujhey us shakhs ke barey mein ijazat dey den ke jisney  ''la Ilaah illallah''  kaha ho aur main usey jahannam se nikal laaun, farmaya : uska aap ko haq hasil nahin, lekin meri izzat , merey jalal , meri kibriyaai aur meri azmat ki qism ! jis shakhs ne  ''la Ilaah illallah'' kaha hoga mein usey us (jahannam) se zarur nikaalunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5574,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat meri shafaat ke lihaz se sab se ziyada sa'adat mand shakhs wo hoga jisney khulus dil se (la Ilaah illallah) ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin'' padha hoga.'' Bukhari."
5575,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas gosht laya gaya to us se eik dasti aap ki khidmat mein pesh ki gaee , jabkey dasti aap ko pasand thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney daanton se eik baar usey nocha , phir farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat main tamam logon ka sardar hunga, us din tamam log Rabul-Aalemin ke huzur khadey hongey, Suraj qarib ho jaeyga, aur log gham aur takleef ki inteha ko pahunch jaeyngey, tamam log kahengey , kya tumhen aisa koi shakhs nazar nahin aata hai jo tumharey rab ke yahan tumhari sifarish karey, chunanche wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey , aur phir aagey hadees shafaat bayan ki, aur farmaya : ''main jaaun ga aur arsh ke nichey pahunchunga to apney rab ke huzur sajda rez ho jaaunga , phir Allah apni hamd aur sanaa ke aisey kalimaat mujhey sikhaeyga jo usney mujh se pehley kisi ko nahin sikhaey hongey, phir wo farmaeyga : Muhammad ! apna sar uthaeyn , sawal karen, aap ka sawal pura kiya jaeyga, aur sifarish karen tumhari sifarish qubul ki jaeygi, main apna sar uthaunga, aur kahunga, rab ji ! meri ummat, rab ji ! meri ummat, rab ji ! meri ummat, kaha jaeyga : Muhammad ! aap apni ummat ke un afrad ko, jin par koi hisab nahin, jannat ke darwaazon mein se daain darwazey se dakhil keejiye, halanke unhen uskey ilawa deegar darwazon se logon ke sath guzarney ka bhi haq hasil hai.'' phir farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! jannat ke darwazey ki dehleez ke darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna Makka aur hijr ke darmiyan hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5576,"Hazrat shafaat se mutalliq Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, farmaya : ''amanat aur sila rehmi ko chhoda jaeyga to wo pul-siraat ke dono kinaron par khadi ho jaeyngi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5577,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sura Ibrahim mein mojud Allah Taala ka ye farman : ''rab ji ! unhoney bahut se logon ko gumrah kiya, jisney meri ittiba ki to wo mujh se hai.'' aur Esa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : ''agar to unhen azab dey to wo terey bandey hain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haath uthaey aur dua ki : ''aey Allah ! meri ummat , meri ummat !'' aur aap roney lagey. Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''Jibrael ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaao , aur tera rab ziyada janta hai, un se poochho ke unhen kon si chiz rulaa rahi hai?'' Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas tashrif laye to aap se daryaft kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo kaha tha wohi unhen bata diya, Allah Taala ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) se farmaya : ''Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaao aur kaho : ham aap ki ummat ke mutalliq aap ko razi kar dengey aur aap ko ghamgin nahin karengey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5578,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kuchh logon ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya roze-qiyamat ham apney rab ko dekhen gey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, kya do-pehar ke waqt , jab aasman par badal na ho to Suraj dekhney main tum koi takleef mehsus kartey ho? aur kya chaudahwin raat jab aasman par badal na ho to tum chaand dekhney mein koi takleef mehsus kartey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usi tarah tum roze-qiyamat Allah ko dekhney mein takleef mehsus nahin karogey, magar jis qadr tum un dono mein se kisi eik ko dekhney mein takleef mehsus kartey ho. jab qiyamat ka din hoga to eik aelan karney wala aelan kerega : her ummat apney mabud ke peechhey chali jaey, Allah ke ilawa asnaam aur buton ki puja karney waley sarey ke sarey aag mein gir jaeyngey yahan tak ke jab sirf Allah ki ibadat karney waley nek aur faajir qism ke log reh jaeyngey to rabul-Aalemin unke paas aaeyga, aur puchheyga, tum kis ka intizar kar rahey ho? her ummat apney mabud ke peechhey ja chuki hai, wo arz karengey : rab ji ! ham ne duniya mein un se alehdgi ikhtiyar kiye rakhi jabkey ham unke zarurat mand they aur ham unke sath na rahey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5579,"Aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''wo kahengey jab tak hamara rab hamarey paas nahin aata tab tak hamari yehi jagah hai, jab hamara rab aa jaeyga ham usey pehchan lengey.'' aur Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''wo farmaeyga : kya tumharey aur uskey darmiyan koi nishani hai jisey tum pehchanteyho? wo arz karengey : ji haan , wo apni pindli zahir kerega to her wo shakhs jo ikhlas ke sath sajda karta tha usey Allah sajdey ki ijazat dey dega aur jo kisi khof, riya kaari ki khatir sajda kiya karta tha Allah uski kamar ko takhta bana dega, jab wo sajda karney ka irada kerega to wo apni guddi ke bal gir jaeyga, uskey baad jahannam par pul rakha jaeyga aur sifarish karney ki ijazat mil jaeygi tamam (Anbiya (Alaihissalam)) kahengey : aey Allah ! salamti farmana , salamti farmana , momin (apney apney aamaal ke mutabiq) kuchh aankh jhapakney ki tarah , kuchh hawa ki raftaar ki tarah , kuchh perindey ki udaan ki tarah , kuchh tez raftaar ghodon ki tarah aur kuchh mukhtalif sawaariyon ki raftaar ki tarah guzrengey , koi to sahih salaamat najat pa jaeyngey aur kisi ko jahannam ki aag mein dhakel diya jaeyga. yahan tak ke momin jahannam ki aag se najat pa jaeyngey, to us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! haq leney ki khatir tum se ziyada shadeed mutalba karney wala koi nahin hoga, jab unhen roze-qiyamat apney bhaiyon ke haq ka pata chaleyga, jo ke jahannam ki aag mein hongey, wo kahengey , hamarey rab ! wo hamarey sath rozey rakha kartey they, hamarey sath namazein padha kartey they aur wo Haj kiya kartey they, unhen kaha jaeyga : jin ko tum pehchantey ho unhen nikal lo , unki Suraton ko jahannam ki aag par haram qarar diya jaeyg , wo bahut si makhluq ko nikalengey, phir wo kahengey, hamarey rab ! jinkey mutalliq to ne hamen hukm diya tha un mein se koi eik bhi baqi nahin raha, wo farmaeyga : dobara jaao aur tum jiskey dil mein Dinar ke barabar bhi khair paao, usko nikal laao, wo bahut sari makhluq ko nikal laeyngey, wo phir farmaeyga : laut jaao aur tum jiskey dil mein nisf (aadhe) Dinar ke barabar bhi khair paao to usko nikal laao, wo bahut sari makhluq ko nikal laeyn gey. wo phir farmaeyga : lot jaao aur tum jiskey dil mein zarra barabar khair paao, usey nikal laao, wo bahut sari makhluq ko nikal laeyn gey, phir wo arz karengey : hamarey rab ! ham ne us (jahannam) mein kisi ehale-khair ko nahin chhoda, (sab ko nikal liya hai) tab Allah farmaeyga : farishton ne sifarish ki, Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ne sifarish ki aur mominon ne sifarish ki sirf sabseziyada reham karne wala hi baqi reh gaya hai, wo jahannamiyon ki eik mutthi bharey ga aur wo us se aisey logon ko nikalega jinhon ne kabhi neki ka koi kaam nahin kiya hoga aur wo koila bin chukey hongey, wo unhen jannat ke darwazon par behney wali nehar mein dalega , usey nehare-hayaat kaha jaeyga, wo is tarah niklengey jis tarah dana sailabi mitti mein ug aata hai, wo motiyon ki tarah niklengey , unki gardanon mein (alamat ke taur par) haar hongey, ehale-jannat kahengey : ye Rehman (Allah taalaa) ke azaad karda hain, usney unhen bila kisi amal ke aur kisi neki ke jis ko unhoney aagey bheja ho, jannat mein dakhil farmaya hai, unke liye kaha jaeyga : tumharey liye (jannat mein) wo kuchh hai jo tum ne (hade nazar tak) dekh liya aur uskey sath itna aur.'' muttafaq aleh."
5580,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab jannati jannat mein aur jahannami jahannam mein chaley jaeyngey to Allah Taala farmaeyga : jiskey dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar eman hai usey nikal lo, unhen nikal liya jaeyga, wo jal kar koila bin chukey hongey, unhen nehare-hayaat mein dal diya jaeyga aur wo us se is tarah namoodaar hongey jis tarah sailabi mitti mein dana ug aata hai, kya tum ne dekha nahin ke wo (dana shuru mein) zard rang ka lipta hua paudaa nikal aata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5581,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke logon ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham roze-qiyamat apney rab ko dekhengey? unhoney Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ka mafhoom bayan kiya, albatta pindli kholney ka zikr nahin kiya, aur farmaya : ''jahannam ke dono kinaron par pul qaaim kiya jaeyga, tamam Rasulon se pehley main apni ummat ke sath us (pul) ko uboor (paar) karunga , us din sirf Rasool hi kalam karengey aur us din Rasulon ka kalam yehi hoga : aey Allah ! salamti ata farmana , aey Allah salamti ata farmana , aur jahannam mein sa'daan ke kaanton ki tarah aankdey hongey, aur un (aankdon) ke tool aur arz ko sirf Allah hi janta hai, wo logon ko unke aamaal ke mutabiq uchak lengey , chunanche un mein se aisey bhi hongey jo halak ho jaeyngey, aur un mein se kuchh aisey bhi hongey jo kaat daley jaeyngey phir (girney sey) bach jaeyngey, yahan tak ke jab Allah apney bandon ke darmiyan faisley se farigh ho jaeyga aur wo jahannam se nikalney ka irada farmaeyga to wo jinhen us se nikalney ka irada farmaeyga wo aisey hongey jo ye gawahi detey hongey ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, wo farishton ko hukm farmaeyga ke Allah ki ibadat karney walon ko nikalen, wo unhen nikalengey , aur wo unhen sajdon ke nishaanaat se pehchan lengey , aur Allah Taala ne aag par haram kar diya hai ke wo sajdon ke nishaanaat (ki jagah)  ko khaye , aag insan ke sajdon ke nishaanaat ke siwa baqi tamam aaza ko kha jaeygi, aur wo aag se nikal liye jaeyngey dar-haalnke wo jal chukey hongey phir un par aabe-hayaat bahaayaa jaeyga aur wo aisey namoodaar hongey jis tarah سsailabi mitti se dana ug aata hai, jannat aur jahannam ke beech eik aadmi baqi reh jaeyga, aur jannat mein dakhil honey wala wo aakhiri jahannami hoga, uska chehra jahannam ki aag ki taraf hoga, wo arz kerega : rab ji ! mera chehra jahannam se dusri taraf kar dey, (kyonkey) uski badboo ne mujhey aziyat mein mubtala kar rakha hai aur uskey sholoon ne mujhey jala diya hai, rab taala farmaeyga : kya aisa to nahin ke agar maine ye kar diya to to uskey ilawa koi dusri chiz ka sawal kar dey, wo arz kerega : teri izzat ki qism ! nahin (koi aur sawal nahin karunga) , wo jo Allah chaheyga , Allah ko ehad aur meesaaq (waada) dega to Allah uskey chehrey ko aag se dusri taraf pher dega , aur jab wo jannat ki taraf munh kar lega aur wo uski ronaq dekhega to jis qadr Allah chaheyga ke wo khamosh rahey to wo is qadr khamosh rahega , phir wo arz kerega : rab ji ! mujhey jannat ke darwazey ke qarib kar dey , Allah tabarak w taala farmaeyga : kya to ne mujh se ehad aur meesaaq (waada) nahin kiya tha ke to us sawal ke baad kisi aur chiz ke mutalliq sawal nahin karega? wo arz karega : rab ji ! main teri makhluq ka sab se ziyada bad nasib shakhs na ho jaaun : chunanche wo farmaeyga : kya ho sakta hai ke agar main tumhen ye ata kar dun to to uskey ilawa kisi dusri chiz ka mutalba kar dey? wo arz kerega : teri izzat ki qism ! (aisey) nahin, main uskey ilawa kisi aur chiz ka tujh se mutalba nahin karunga, wo apney rab ko, jo Allah Taala chaheyga ehad aur meesaaq (waada) dega , to wo usey jannat ke darwazey ke qarib kar dega , aur jab wo uskey darwazey par pahunch jaeyga, to wo uski taro-taazagi, aur is mein jo ronaq aur suroor dekhega to jis qadr Allah chaheyga ke wo khamosh rahey to wo khamosh rahega , phir arz kerega : rab ji ! mujhey jannat mein dakhil farma dey , Allah tabarak w taala farmaeyga : ibne-Adam ! tujh par afsos hai, to kitna bada wada khilaf hai ! kya to ne ehad aur meesaaq (waada) nahin diya tha ke to us chiz ke ilawa , jo maine tumhen ata kar di, koi dusri chiz ka mutalba nahin kerega? wo arz kerega : rab ji ! mujhey apni makhluq mein sab se ziyada bad nasib na bana, wo musalsal dua karta rahega yahan tak ke Allah uski wajeh se hans dega, jab wo hans dega to wo usey jannat mein dakhil hone ki ijazat farma dega , aur farmaeyga : tamanna kar , wo tamanna kerega yahan tak ke jab uski tamannaeyn khatam ho jaeyngi to Allah Taala farmaeyga : to falan falan chiz ki tamanna kar , uska rab usey yad dilaaeyga, yahan tak ke jab ye sab tamannaeyn khatam ho jaeyngi to Allah farmaeyga, ye (jo to ne tamanna ki)  terey liye hai aur itni hi mazeed uskey sath (tujhey ata ki jati hain).'' aur Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''Allah farmaeyga : ye (jo to ne tamanna ki) terey liye hai aur uski jaisi das guna mazeed (ata ki jati hain).'' muttafaq aleh."
5582,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se aakhir mein jannat mein dakhil honey wala aadmi wo hoga jo eik baar chalega aur eik baar munh ke bal gireyga aur eik baar aag usey jhulseygi, jab wo us (aag) se guzar jaeyga to wo uski taraf mud kar dekh kar kahega, ba-barkat hai wo zaat jisney mujhey tujh se bacha liya aur Allah ne mujhey wo chiz ata farma di jo usney aglon aur pichlon mein se kisi ko ata nahin farmaee, usey eik darkht dikhaya jaeyga to wo arz kerega : rab ji ! mujhey us darkht ke qarib kar dey ta ke main uskey saye se saya hasil kar sakun , aur uskey (paas chashmey ke pani sey) pani pi sakoon, Allah farmaeyga : ibne-Adam ! shayad ke main wo tujhey ata kar dun to phir tum uskey ilawa kisi aur chiz ka mutalba karogey, wo arz kerega : rab ji ! nahin, wo us se muahida kerega ke wo us se uskey ilawa kisi aur chiz ka mutalba nahin kerega, aur uska rab (sawal karney par) usey mazoor samjheyga, kyonkey wo aisi chizon ka mushaahida karega jinhen dekh kar wo sabr nahin kar sakega, wo usko us (darkht) ke qarib kar dega to wo uskey saye se saya hasil kerega aur uskey (chashmey) se pani piyega, phir usey eik aur darkht dikhaya jaeyga jo pehley se bhi kahin ziyada khoobsurat hoga, wo arz kerega : rab ji ! mujhey us darkht ke qarib kar dey ta ke main uskey (chashmey ke) pani se pani pi sakun aur uskey saye se saya hasil kar sakoon, aur main uskey ilawa tujh se aur koi chiz nahin maangunga , wo farmaeyga : ibne-Adam ! kya to ne mujh se wada nahin kiya tha ke to uskey ilawa mujh se koi aur chiz nahin maangeyga , aur wo farmaeyga : ho sakta hai ke main tujhey uskey qarib kar dun to phir to mujh se uskey ilawa koi aur chiz mang ley, wo us sey, uskey ilawa koi aur chiz na maangney ka wada kar lega , jabkey uska rab usey (dobara sawal karney par) mazoor samjheyga, kyonkey wo aisi nematon ka mushaahida kerega jinhen dekh kar uska pemanae-sabr labrez ho jaeyga, wo usko uskey qarib kar dega to wo uskey saye se saya hasil kerega, aur uskey (chashmey ke) pani se pani piyega . phir jannat ke darwazey par usey eik aur darkht dikhaya jaeyga jo sabiqa dono darakhton se kahin ziyada khoobsurat hoga, ye arz kerega : rab ji ! mujhey us (darkht) ke qarib kar dey taa-ke main uskey saye se saya hasil kar sakun aur uskey (chashmey ke) pani se pani piyun, phir main uskey ilawa tujh se koi sawal nahin karunga, wo farmaeyga : ibne-Adam ! kya tune mujh se muahida nahin kiya tha ke to iskey ilawa mujh se koi aur chiz nahin maangeyga, wo arz kerega : rab ji ! bilkul theek hai, bas ye pura farma dey, main uskey ilawa koi aur sawal nahin karunga, uska rab usey mazoor samjheyga, phir wo aisi nematon ka mushaahida kerega jinhen dekh kar wo sabr nahin kar sakega , wo uskey qarib kar dega , jab wo usey uskey qarib kar dega to wo ehle jannat ki aawazen suneyga to arz kerega, rab ji ! mujhey is mein dakhil farma dey , wo farmaeyga : ibne-Adam ! kon si chiz (chaahne ke baad) to mujh se sawal karna tarak kerega? kya to razi ho jaeyga ke main duniya ke barabar aur uski jaisi mazeed tujhey ata kar dun? wo arz kerega : rab ji ! kya aap mujh se mazaq kartey ho jabkey aap Rabul-Aalemin ho?'' ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hans diye, aur farmaya : kya tum mujh se sawal nahin karogey ke main kis wajeh se hans raha hun? unhoney puchha ke aap kyon hans rahey hain? unhoney farmaya : isi tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi hansey they, is par Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya tha, Allah ke Rasool ! aap kis wajeh se hans rahey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Rabul-Aalemin ke hansney ki wajeh se jab usney kaha tha, kya to mujh se mazaq karta hai jabkey to Rabul-Aalemin hai? wo farmaeyga : main tujh se mazaq nahin karta balke main jo chahun uskey karney par qadir hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
5583,"Aur Sahih Muslim hi ki Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees isi tarah hai, albatta unhoney ye zikr nahin kiya : ''wo farmaeyga : ibne-Adam ! kon si chiz tujhey mujh se (sawal karney sey) baaz rakhey gi?'' aakhir hadees tak , aur is mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''Allah usey yad karaaeyga, falan chiz maango , falan chiz maango , yahan tak ke jab uski khaahishat khatam ho jaeyngi to Allah Taala farmaeyga : wo (jo to ne manga) terey liye hai aur us se das guna mazeed terey liye hai.'' farmaya : ''phir wo apney ghar mein dakhil hoga to hur-ain se uski do biwiyan uskey paas ayengi, to wo kahengi : her qism ki hamd aur shukr Allah ke liye hai jisney tujhey hamari khatir aur hamein teri khatir paida farmaya.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (banda) kahega : jo mujhey ata kiya gaya hai wesa kisi aur ko ata nahin kiya gaya.'' rawahu Muslim."
5584,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kuchh log un gunahon ki wajeh se jo unhoney kiye hongey bator saza aag unhen jhulas deygi, phir Allah apney Fazal aur rehmat se unhen jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga, unhen jahannami kaha jaeyga.'' Bukhari."
5585,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki shafaat ke zariey kuchh logon ko jahannam ki aag se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil kar diya jaeyga, unka naam jahannami rakha jaeyga.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''meri ummat ke kuchh log meri shafaat ke zariey jahannam ki aag se nikaley jaeyngey h, unka naam jahannami rakha jaeyga.'' Bukhari aur Tirmizi."
5586,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main achhi tarah janta hun ke jahannamiyon mein se sab se aakhir par us (jahannam) se kon nikleyga aur sab se aakhir par jannat mein kon dakhil hoga, eik aadmi peeth ke bal ghisat kar jahannam se niklega to Allah farmaeyga : ja, jannat mein dakhil ho ja , wo wahan aaeyga to usey aisey khayal aaeyga ke wo to bhar chuki hai, wo arz kerega : rab ji ! maine to usey bhara hua paya hai, Allah farmaeyga , ja , jannat mein dakhil ho ja , terey liye duniya aur uski jaisi das guna hai, wo arz kerega : kya to mujh se mazaq karta hai, halanke to badshah hai.'' (raawi bayan kartey hain) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap hans diye yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagin, kaha jata hai ke wo jannat ka sab se kam darjey wala shakhs hoga. muttafaq aleh."
5587,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main achhi tarah janta hun jo sab se aakhir mein jannat mein dakhil hoga aur jo sab se aakhir mein jahannam se nikleyga, eik aadmi ko roze-qiyamat pesh kiya jaeyga to kaha jaeyga, is par uskey sagheera gunah pesh karo aur uskey kabeera gunah chupa rakho, uskey sagheera gunah is par pesh kiye jaeyngey to kaha jaeyga : falan din to ne ye , ye , ye aur ye kiya aur falan din tu ney ye , ye , ye aur ye kiya, wo arz kerega : ji haan ! wo inkar nahin kar sakega , aur wo apney kabeera gunahon se dar raha hoga ke wo is par pesh kiye jaeyngey, itney mein usey kaha jaeyga : her burai ke badley tujhey neki ata ki jati hai, to wo arz kerega : rab ji ! maine to kuchh aisey (kabeera) gunah kiye they jinhen main yahan dekh nahin raha.'' aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap hans diye yahan tak ke aap ki daadhein nazar aaney lagin. rawahu Muslim."
5588,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(sab se aakhir par) jahannam se chaar aadmiyon ko nikal kar Allah ke huzur pesh kiya jaeyga, wo phir unhen jahannam mein ley janey ka hukm farmaeyga, un mein se eik phir mud mud kar dekhega aur arz kerega : rab ji ! main to ummid karta tha ke jab to ne mujhey wahan se nikal liya to phir to mujhey is mein nahin lotayega .'' farmaya : ''Allah usko us (jahannam) se najat dey-dega.'' rawahu Muslim."
5589,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin jahannam se khulaasi hasil kar lengey to unhen jannat aur jahannam ke darmiyan eik pul par rok liya jaeyga aur unke duniya ke bahami (aapsi) malazim (haq-talfiyon) ka eik doosrey se badla dilaaya jaeyga yahan tak ke jab wo saaf suthrey kar diye jaeyngey to unhen jannat mein dakhil honey ki ijazat di jaeygi, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! un mein se her eik jannat mein apney ghar ko , duniya mein apney ghar ke muqabley mein ziyada behtar tareeqey se janta hoga.'' Bukhari."
5590,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein dakhil honey se pehley her shakhs ko uska jahannam ka thikana bhi dikhaya jaeyga ke agar usney nafarmani ki hoti (to uska thikana wo hota) ta ke wo mazeed shukr karey, aur (usi tarah) jahannam mein dakhil honey waley her shakhs ka usko jannat ka thikana bhi dikhaya jaeyga, agar usney achhey amal kiye hotey (to uska thikana ye hota) ta ke wo uskey liye hasrat aur afsos ka baais ho.'' Bukhari."
5591,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab jannati jannat mein aur jahannami jahannam mein chaley jaeyngey to maut ko laya jaeyga aur usey jannat aur jahannam ke darmiyan khada kar diya jaeyga, phir usey zibeh kar diya jaeyga, phir eik aelan karney wala aelan kerega : jannat walo ! (ab) maut naam ki koi chiz nahin, jahannam walo ! (ab) maut koi nahin, jannatiyon ki farhat mein , jabkey jahannamiyon ke huzn aur malaal mein izafa hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5592,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey hoz ki lambaai aur chaudaai adn aur bilqaa ke amaan ki darmiyani masafat (doori) jitna hoga, uska pani doodh se ziyada safed aur shehad se ziyada mitha hoga, uskey piyaley aasman ke sitaron ki tadaad ke barabar hongey, jisney us se eik baar pi liya to uskey baad wo piyasa nahin hoga, wahan sab se pehley fuqra muhajrin ka wrood hoga unke sar ke baal bikhrey hongey, kapdey maile hongey, ye wo log hongey jinhonne naaz aur nemat wali aurton se nikah kiya hoga na unke liye darwazey kholey jatey they.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
5593,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, ham ne eik jagah padaaw dala to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo log hoz par merey paas aaeyngey tum unka laakhwan hissey ho.'' (Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey) puchha gaya is roz tum kitney they? unhoney farmaya : saat so ya aath so. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
5594,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her Nabi ke liye eik hoz hai, aur wo is baat par baham (aapas mein) fakhr karengey ke un mein se kis ke paas ziyada peeney waley aatey hain, main ummid karta hun ke un sab mein se merey paas aaney walon ki tadaad ziyada hogi.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5595,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se darkhast ki, roze-qiyamat wo meri sifarish farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main kar dunga.'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! (sifarish ke liye) mein aap ko kahan talash karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum sab se pehley mujhey pal siraat par talash karna.'' maine arz kya : agar main pal siraat par aap se mulaqat na karun ( to phir) ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir mujhey meezaan ke paas talash karna.'' maine arz kya, agar main meezaan ke paas aap ko na paaon? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hoz ke paas talash karna , kyonkey mein un teen jagahon ke ilawa kahin nahin hunga.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5596,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke maqame-Mehmood kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye wo din hai jab Allah Taala apni kursi par nuzool farmaeyga to wo (kursi) apni tangi ki wajeh se is tarah char char ki aawaz nikaley gi jis tarah naee zeen char-char ki aawaz nikaalti hai, halanke wo (kursi) zamin w aasman ke darmiyan masafat ki tarah wasee hai. tum nangey paaon, nangey badan aur khatnon ke baghair laye jaaogey , sab se pehley Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko libas pehnaya jaeyga, Allah Taala farmaeyga : merey khaleel ko libas pehnao, aap ko jannat ki chaadaron mein se do safed chadaren di jaeyngi, phir unke baad mujhey libas pehnaya jaeyga, phir main Allah ke daain taraf eik jagah khada ho jaaunga, tamam agley pichley mujh par rashk karengey.'' rawahu Darmi ."
5597,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat mominon ka pal siraat par ye shiaar (nishan pehchan) hoga : ''rab ji! salamti ata farma, salamti ata farma.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5598,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri shafaat, meri ummat ke un afrad ke liye hai jo kabeera gunah kartey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
5599,aur ibne-Maja ne Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja.
5600,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey rab ki taraf se aaney wala eik merey paas aaya to usney mujhey ikhtiyar diya ke aap apni nisf ummat jannat mein dakhil kar lein ya shafaat ka haq ley lein, maine shafaat ko ikhtiyar kar liya, aur wo us shakhs ke liye hai jo us haalat mein faut hua ke wo Allah ke sath kisi aur ko shareek na thehrata ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja."
5601,"Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Jadaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat ke eik aadmi (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) ki sifarish par qabila bano Tameem se ziyada afrad jannat mein jaeyngey.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi w ibne-Maja."
5602,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein se baaz eik jamaat ki sifarish karengey, un mein se baaz qabiley ki, un mein se baaz eik khandan ki aur un mein se koi kisi aadmi ki sifarish kerega yahan tak ke (is tarah sifarish kartey kartey ( wo jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyngey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5603,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall ne mujh se wada kya hai ke wo meri ummat se chaar lakh afrad ko baghair hisab jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga.'' abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! izafa farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur is tarah, aapney apney dono haathon se chullu banaya , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! hamari is tadaad mein bhi izafa farmaeyn. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur is tarah. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : abu-Bakar ! hamen chhod do , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar Allah ham sab ko jannat mein dakhil farma dey to tumhara kya nuqsan hai? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar Allah azz-w-jall chahey ke wo apni makhluq ko eik chullu ke zariey jannat mein dakhil farma dey to wo kar sakta hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umar ne theek kaha hai.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
5604,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannamiyon ki saf banai jaeygi to jannat walon mein se aadmi unke paas se guzrega to un mein se eik aadmi kahega : aey falan! kya tum mujhey pehchantey nahin? main wohi hun jisney eik martaba tujhey pani pilaya tha, aur un mein se koi kahega : main wohi hun jisney wuzu ke liye pani diya tha, wo uskey liye sifarish kerega to wo usey jannat mein) apney sath ( dakhil karaaeyga .'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5605,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam mein janey walon mein se do aadmi bahut zor se aah w bukaa (cheekh-pukar) kar rahey hongey, rab taala farmaeyga : un dono ko nikalo , wo unhen farmaeyga : tum kis wajeh se zor zor se cheekh rahey ho? wo arz karengey , ham ne ye isliye kya hai taake aap ham par rehem farmaeyn, Allah Taala farmaeyga : tumharey liye meri rehmat yehi hai ke tum chaley jaao aur tum jahannam mein jahan they apney aap ko wahin dal do, un mein se eik apney aap ko) jahannam mein) dal lega , Allah usko is par thandi aur salamti wali bana dega , jabkey doosra khada rahega , aur wo apney aap ko) jahannam mein) nahin dalega, rab taala us se pucheyga : kis chiz ne tujhey apney aap ko jahannam mein dalney se mana kya jaisa ke terey sathi ne (apney aap ko) dal liya? wo arz kerega : rab ji! main ummid karta hun ke to mujhey wahan nahin bhejega jahan se tu ney mujhey nikal liya tha, rab taala usey farmaeyga : tumharey liye tumhari ummid ke mutabiq ata kar diya gaya, wo dono Allah ki rehmat se ikhattey hi jannat mein dakhil kiye jaeyngey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
5606,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tamam log aag (pul siraat) par waarid hongey, phir wo apney aamaal ke mutabiq wahan se paar hongey, un mein se sab se pehley bijli chamakney ki manind guzar jaeyngey, phir hawa ki manind, phir tez raftaar ghodey ki manind, phir sawari par Sawar ki manind, phir dodney waley aadmi ki manind aur phir pedal chalney waley ki manind (us pul se guzrengey jo ke jahannam par nasab hoga).'' rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi ."
5607,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey aagey mera hoz hai, uskey dono kinaron ke darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna jarba aur Azrah ke darmiyan hai.'' baaz raawiyon ne kaha hai : ye dono (jarbaa aur Azrah) Sham ke do gaaon hain. un dono ke darmiyan teen raaton ki masafat hai. eik riwayat mein hai : uskey piyaley aasman ke sitaron ki tarah hain, jo koi wahan aaeyga aur us se pani pi lega to phir uskey baad wo kabhi piyas mehsus nahin kerega.'' muttafaq aleh."
5608,"Hazrat Huzefa aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tabarak w taala tamam logon ko jama farmaeyga to momin khadey hongey yahan tak ke unke liye jannat qarib kar di jaeygi, wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey aur arz karengey : hamarey abba jaan ! hamarey liye jannat khulney ki darkhast karen, wo kahengey : tumharey walid ki ghalati hi ne to tumhen jannat se nikalwaaya tha, mein uskey ehle nahin hun, tum merey bete Allah ke khaleel Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao, farmaya : '' Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) farmaeyngey : main bhi uskey ehl nahin hun main to bahut pehley ( duniya mein) khaleel tha, tum Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao jis se Allah Taala ne kalam farmaya hai, wo Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey, to wo bhi kahengey , main uskey ehle nahin hun, tum Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao jo Allah ka kalma aur uski rooh hain, Esa (Alaihissalam) bhi kahengey : main uskey ehl nahin hun, wo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaeyngey, wo khadey hongey, unhen ijazat di jaeygi, amanat aur sila rehmi ko bheja jaeyga, wo pul siraat ke dono taraf khadi ho jaeyngi, tum mein se pehla bijli ki tarah guzar jaeyga '' raawi bayan kartey hain maine arz kya : merey waliden aap par qurban hon, bijli ki tarah guzarney ki kya surat hogi ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne bijli nahin dekhi , wo aankh jhapakney mein guzarti hai aur wapis aa jati hai. phir hawa ke chalney ki tarah, phir perindey ki tarah aur tez chalney waley aadmiyon ki tarah, unke aamaal unhen lekar chalengey, aur tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pul siraat par khadey hongey, wo keh rahey hongey : rab ji ! salamti ata farma, salamti ata farma : yahan tak ke bandon ke aamaal aajiz aa jaeyngey. yahan tak ke eik aisa aadmi aaeyga jo chalney ki taqat nahin rakhta hoga, balke wo peeth ke bal ghisat raha hoga.'' aur farmaya : '' pul siraat ke dono kinaron par aankdey muallaq hongey, wo is baat par maamoor hongey ke jiskey mutalliq usey hukm diya jaeyga wo usey pakad lengey, kuch log majrooh hongey, najat pane-waley hongey, aur kuch jahannam mein dhakel diye jaeyngey.'' aur us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki jaan hai! jahannam ki gehraai sattar saal ki masafat hai. rawahu Muslim ."
5609,"Hazrat Huzefa aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tabarak w taala tamam logon ko jama farmaeyga to momin khadey hongey yahan tak ke unke liye jannat qarib kar di jaeygi, wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey aur arz karengey : hamarey abba jaan ! hamarey liye jannat khulney ki darkhast karen, wo kahengey : tumharey walid ki ghalati hi ne to tumhen jannat se nikalwaaya tha, main iskey ehl nahin hun, tum merey bete Allah ke khaleel Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao , farmaya : '' Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) farmaeyngey : main bhi iskey ehl nahin hun main to bahut pehley ( duniya mein) khaleel tha, tum Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao jis se Allah Taala ne kalam farmaya hai, wo Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeyngey , to wo bhi kahengey , main iskey ehl nahin hun, tum Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jaao jo Allah ka kalma aur uski rooh hain, Esa (Alaihissalam) bhi kahengey : main iskey ehl nahin hun, wo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaeyngey, wo khadey hongey, unhen ijazat di jaeygi, amanat aur sila rehmi ko bheja jaeyga, wo pul siraat ke dono taraf khadi ho jaeyngi, tum mein se pehla bijli ki tarah guzar jaeyga '' raawi bayan kartey hain maine arz kya : merey waliden aap par qurban hon, bijli ki tarah guzarney ki kya surat hogi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne bijli nahin dekhi, wo aankh jhapakney mein guzarti hai aur wapis aa jati hai. phir hawa ke chalney ki tarah, phir perindey ki tarah aur tez chalney waley aadmiyon ki tarah, unke aamaal unhen lekar chalengey, aur tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pul siraat par khadey hongey, wo keh rahey hongey : rab ji! salamti ata farma , salamti ata farma : yahan tak ke bandon ke aamaal aajiz aa jaeyngey . yahan tak ke eik aisa aadmi aaeyga jo chalney ki taqat nahin rakhta hoga, balke wo peeth ke bal ghisat raha hoga .'' aur farmaya : '' pul siraat ke dono kinaron par aankdey muallaq hongey, wo is baat par maamoor hongey ke jiskey mutalliq usey hukm diya jaeyga wo usey pakad lengey, kuch log majrooh hongey, najat pane-waley hongey, aur kuch jahannam mein dhakel diye jaeyngey .'' aur us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki jaan hai ! jahannam ki gehraai sattar saal ki masafat hai. rawahu Muslim ."
5610,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kuch log jahannam se shafaat ke zariey niklengey goya wo ثغاریر hain.'' ham ne arz kya : ثغاریر kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo lakdiyan hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
5611,"Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roze-qiyamat teen qism ke log sifarish karengey , Anbiya (Alaihissalam) , phir ulama aur phir shohda.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
5612,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne farmaya : maine apney Saleh bandon ke liye (jannat mein) aisi chizen tayyar kar rakhi hain jo na to kisi aankh ne dekhi hain aur na kisi kaan ne suni hain, aur na hi kisi insan ke dil mein unka khayal guzra hai.'' agar tum chaho to ye aayat padho : '' koi nafs nahin janta ke unki aakhon ki thandak ke liye kya chiz chupa kar rakhi gaee hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5613,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat main eik kodey jitni jagah , duniya aur is mein jo kuch hai, sab se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5614,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein subh ko ya Sham ko chalna duniya aur is mein jo kuch hai, sab se behtar hai. agar ehle jannat ki aurton mein se eik aurat zamin par jhank ley to un dono (zameen w aasman) ke darmiyan her chiz roshan ho jaey, un dono ke darmiyan jo kuch hai wo muattar ho jaey aur us (aurat) ke sar ka eik dupatta duniya aur is mein jo kuch hai sab se behtar hai.'' Bukhari ."
5615,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat mein aisa darkht hai jiskey saye mein ghud sawar so saal chalta rahey to wo usey tey nahin kar sakega, aur jannat mein kamaan ke barabar jagah us chiz se behtar hai jis par Suraj tulu hota hai ya ghurub hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5616,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin ke liye jannat main eik khaul daar moti ka khema hoga jis ka arz .'' aur eik riwayat mein hai, uska tool saath mail hoga, uskey her koney mein uskey ehle khana hongey, wo dusron ko nahin dekhengey, momin un sab ke paas jaeyga, aur (uskey liye) do baagh hain, unke bartan aur jo kuch un dono mein hai wo sab chaandi ka hai, aur do baagh hain, un dono ke bartan aur unke darmiyan jo kuch hai wo sab soney ka hai, ehle jannat aur unke rab ke beech sirf kibriyaai ki chadar hai jo ke sada bahar jannat mein uskey chehrey par hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5617,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat mein so darjey hain, aur her do darjon ke darmiyan is qadr fasla hai jis qadr aasman aur zamin ke darmiyan hai, aur firdous sab se aa'laa darjey ki jannat hai, jannat ki chaaron nehren wahin se jari hoti hain aur usi ke ooper arsh hai, jab tum Allah se sawal karo to us se firdous ka sawal karo. (jo ke jannat ka aa'laa maqam hai).'' Tirmizi. maine usey na to sahihain mein paya hai aur na kitabul-humedi mein. rawahu Tirmizi ."
5618,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat main eik ( Juma ( baazar hai, jahan wo her Jumey aaeyngey , shimaal ki taraf se hawa chalegi to wo unke chehron aur unke kapdon mein) khushbu ( daley gi ( jis sey) unke Hasan w jamaal mein izafa ho jaeyga aur jab wo apney ehle khana ke paas jaeyngey to unka Hasan w jamaal badh chuka hoga chunanche unke ehle khana unhen kahengey : Allah ki qism ! tum hamarey baad Hasan w jamaal mein badh chukey ho wo kahengey , Allah ki qism ! tum bhi hamarey baad Hasan w jamaal mein badh chukey ho.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5619,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pehla giroh jo jannat mein dakhil hoga unki soorten chaudahwin raat ke chaand ki tarah roshan hongi, phir unke baad dakhil honey walon ki soorten aasman ke sab se ziyada roshan sitarey ki tarah hongi, (mohabbat w ittifaq ke lihaz sey) unke dil fard wahid ke dil ki tarah hongey, un mein bahami (aapsi) ikhtilaf hoga na koi bahami (aapsi) bughz hoga, un mein se her shakhs ke liye badi aakhon wali hooron mein se do biwiyan hongi. wo is qadr Husain hongi ke unki pindliyon ka gooda haddiyon aur gosht mein nazar aata , wo subh w Sham Allah ki tasbih bayan kartey hongey, wo bimar hongey na peshab karengey, unhen pakhaney ki hajat hogi na unhen thook aaeygi aur na hi naak se aalaaish niklegi, unke bartan soney aur chaandi ke hongey, unki kanghiyaan soney ki hongi, unki angeethiyon ka endhan khushbu daar aud hoga, unka paseena kastoori ki tarah hoga, wo takhleeq ke lihaz se barabar hongey jaisey fard wahid hon, aur wo apney walid Adam (Alaihissalam) ke qad w qaamat par 60-60 haath unchey hongey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5620,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannati jannat mein khaeyn paiyengey lekin wo thookengey na unhen peshab-pakhaney ki hajat hogi aur na hi unki naak se aalaaish nikleygi.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : to phir khana kidhar jaeyga? farmaya : ''dakaar aur paseena, aur paseena kastoori ki tarah hoga, wo is tarah (aasani aur tasalsul ke sath ( tasbih w tahmeed karengey jis tarah tum saans letey ho.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5621,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs jannat mein dakhil hoga wo khushhal rahega, bad haal nahin hoga, na to uska libas puraanaa hoga aur na uski jawani khatam hogi.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5622,"Hazrat abu-Saeed aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (jannat mein) eik aelan karney wala aelan kerega : ''ab tum sehatmand hi rahogey kabhi bimar nahin hogey, tum hamesha zinda rahogey kabhi marogey nahin, hamesha jawan rahogey kabhi boodhey nahin hogey, aur tum hamesha khushhal rahogey kabhi bad-haal nahin hogey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
5623,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(jannat mein) eik aelan karney wala aelan kerega : ''ab tum sehat mand hi rahogey kabhi bimar nahin hogey, tum hamesha zinda rahogey kabhi marogey nahin, hamesha jawan rahogey kabhi boodhey nahin hogey, aur tum hamesha khushhal rahogey kabhi bad-haal nahin hogey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5624,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat waley apney ooper baala khaanon ke makeenon (rehne walon) ko is tarah dekhengey jis tarah tum mashriq ya maghrib ke ufuq mein chamaktey huey doobtey sitarey ko dekhtey ho, aur ye tumharey baham (aapas mein) maraatib mein farq ki wajeh se hoga.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ye Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ki manzilen hongi , jahan unke ilawa koi aur nahin pahunch sakega? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke , us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! wo log jo Allah par eman laye aur unhoney Rasulon ki tasdeeq ki.'' muttafaq aleh."
5625,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat main kuchh aisey log dakhil hongey jinkey dil (hasad aur bughz waghera se paak honey ke lihaz sey) parindon ke dilon ki tarah hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5626,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ehle jannat se farmaeyga : jannat walo ! wo arz karengey : hamarey rab ! ham hazir hain teri sa'adat hasil karney ke liye , aur her qism ki khair aur bhalai terey haathon mein hai, wo farmaeyga : kya tum khush ho? wo arz karengey, rab ji ! hamarey razi na honey ki kya wajeh ho sakti hai jabkey aapney hamein wo kuchh ata farma diya hai jo aapney apni makhluq mein se kisi ko ata nahin farmaya , wo farmaeyga : kya main tumhen us se bhi behtar chiz na dun? wo arz karengey : rab ji ! us se behtar chiz kon si hai? wo farmaeyga : main tumhen apni daaimi razamandi ata karta hun aur main uskey baad tum par kabhi naraz nahin hunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5627,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat main tum mein sab se kam milkiyat wala shakhs wo hoga jisey Allah Taala farmaeyga : tamanna kar ! wo tamanna karega , aur tamanna karega to wo us se puchheyga : kya to ne tamanna kar li? wo kahega , ji haan , to usey kaha jaeyga : tumharey liye wo hai jo to ne tamanna ki aur jo to ne tamanna ki itna uskey sath aur bhi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5628,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''saihaan , jeehaan , faraat aur neel sab jannat ki nehren hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
5629,"Hazrat Utba bin Ghazawaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, hamein bataya gaya ke agar jahannam ke kinarey se pathar giraya jaey to wo sattar saal mein bhi uski teh tak nahin pahunchta , Allah ki qism ! usey bhara jaeyga. hamein ye bhi bataya gaya ke jannat ki chaukhat ka darmiyani fasla chaalis saal ka hai. aur is par eik din aisa bhi aaeyga ke wo azdahaam (bheed) ki wajeh se bhari hogi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5630,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! makhluq ko kis chiz se paida kiya gaya? farmaya : ''pani se.'' ham ne arz kiya : jannat ki taamir kaisey hui? farmaya : ''eik eent soney ki aur eik chaandi ki, uska gaara tez khushbu wali kastoori ka hai, uski chips heerey jawahraat aur yaqoot hain, uski mitti Zaafran hai, jo is mein dakhil hoga wo khushhal rahega , bad-haal nahin hoga, wahan hamesha rahega , faut nahin hoga, uskey kapdey boseedah hongey na uski jawani khatam hogi.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Darmi."
5631,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat ke darakhton ke taney soney ke hongey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5632,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein sau darjey hain, her do darjon ke darmiyan sau saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5633,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein sau darjey hain, agar tamam jahan waley un mein se kisi eik mein jama ho jaeyn to wo unke liye kafi ho.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5634,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Allah Taala ke farman : (وَ فُرُشٍ مَّرْفُوْعَۃٍ) ''aur buland bistare'' ke barey mein riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un (bichhonon) ki bulandi is tarah hogi jis tarah zamin aur aasman ke darmiyan fasla hai, aur wo fasla paanch sau saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5635,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pehla giroh jo roze-qiyamat jannat mein jaeyga unke chehrey is tarah roshan hongey jis tarah chaudahwin raat ka chaand roshan hota hai, doosra giroh aasman mein sab se ziyada chamak daar sitarey ki tarah roshan hoga, un mein se her aadmi ke liye do biwiyan hongi, her biwi par sattar jodey hongey, uski pindli ka goodaa unke ooper se nazar aaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5636,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ko jannat mein jima (sambhog) ki bahut ziyada taqat di jaeygi.'' arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya wo uski taqat rakhega? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : usey sau (aadmiyon) ki taqat di jaeygi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5637,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar jannat ki nematon mein se nakhun barabar koi nemat (duniya mein) zahir ho jaey to uski wajeh se zamin aur aasman ke kinarey muzayyan ho (saj) jaeyn , aur agar jannat walon mein se eik aadmi (zameen par) jhank dey aur uskey kangan zahir ho jaeyn to uski roshni Suraj ki roshni ko is tarah mita dey jis tarah Suraj sitaron ki roshni mita deta hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5638,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat walon ke jism par baal na hongey aur na unki dadhi hogi, aur unki aankhen surmai rang ki hongi, na to unki jawaaniyaan khatam hongi aur na unke kapdey boseedah hongey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
5639,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat waley jannat mein us haal mein dakhil hongey ke na to unke jism par baal hongey aur na unki dadhi hogi , unki aankhen surmai rang ki hongi aur unki umr tees ya tentis saal hogi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5640,"Hazrat Asma binte-Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna, aap se sidratul-muntaha ka zikr kiya gaya to farmaya : ''sawar uski shaakhon ke saye mein sau saal chalta rahega.'' ya farmaya : ''uskey saye se sau sawar saya hasil kar saken gey.'' is mein raawi ko shak hua hai.'' is par patingey soney ke hongey, aur uska phal badey matkon ki tarah hoga.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5641,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya, kausar kiya chiz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo eik nehar hai jo Allah ne mujhey ata ki hai, yani wo mujhey jannat ata karega, (us ka pani) doodh se ziyada safed , shehad se ziyada mitha hai, us main eik perinda hai jiski gardan oont ki gardan ki tarah hai.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : ye to phir bahut achchhi nemat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usko khaney waley us se bhi ziyada achchhey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5642,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya jannat mein ghodey hongey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar Allah ne tujhey jannat mein dakhil kar diya aur to ne agar wahan surkh yaqoot ke ghodey par Sawar honey ki khahish ki to wo jannat mein jahan to chaheyga tujhey uda kar ley jaeyga.'' eik doosrey aadmi ne aap se daryaft kartey huey arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya jannat mein oont bhi hongey? raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey wo jawab nahin diya jo aapney uskey sathi ko jawab diya tha (balke) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar Allah ne tujhey jannat mein dakhil farma diya to terey liye wahan wo kuchh hoga jis ko tera dil chaheyga aur (jis sey) teri aankhen lazzat aur suroor hasil karengin.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5643,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main (duniya mein) ghodey pasand karta hun, kya jannat mein ghodey hongey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tujhey jannat mein dakhil kar diya gaya to tujhey yaqoot ka eik ghoda diya jaeyga, jiskey do par hongey, tujhey is par Sawar kiya jaeyga, phir to jahan chaheyga wo tujhey uda ley jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : is hadees ki sanad qawi nahin, Abu Sura raawi hadees ke mamley mein zaeef qarar diya gaya hai, maine Imam Bukhari se suna, wo farma rahey they ye munkar hadees hai, aur wo munkir riwayaat bayan karta hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5644,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat walon ki eik sau bees safein hongi , un mein se assi is ummat ki hongi , aur chaalis baqi tamam ummaton ki hongi.'' (rawahu Tirmizi, Darmi, al-Behaqi fi kitab al-ba's aur Nushur)."
5645,"Hazrat Salim (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke log jis darwazey se jannat mein dakhil hongey, uska arz, behtareen sawar ki teen (roz ya saal) ki masafat (doori) ke barabar hai, phir bhi wahan se dakhil hotey waqt wo itney tang hongey ke qarib hai ke unke kandhey alag ho jaeyn.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees zaeef hai, aur maine Muhammad bin Ismail (Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu)) se is hadees ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney isey na pehchaana aur farmaya : Yakhlud-bin-Abi-Bakr munkir riwayaat bayan karta hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5646,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat main eik baazar hai, wahan koi kharid aur farokht nahin hogi , albatta wahan mardon aur aurton ki taswiren hongi , jab aadmi kisi surat aur tasweer ko pasand kerega to wo is mein dakhil ho jaeyga.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5647,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwaayat hai ke wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se miley to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main Allah se darkhast karta hun ke wo (Madina ke baazar ki tarah) mujh ko aur aap ko jannat ke baazar mein ikhatta farmaey, Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya wahan baazar hoga? unhoney farmaya : haan , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''jab jannat waley, us (jannat) mein dakhil ho jaeyngey to wo apney aamaal ke hisab se wahan qiyam karengey, phir duniya ke dinon se Jume ke din ki miqdaar ke mutabiq unhen ijazat di jaeygi to wo apney rab ki ziyaarat karengey aur wo unke liye apna arsh zahir farmaeyga, wo (unka rab) unki khatir jannat ke baaghon mein se eik baagheechey mein tajalli farmaeyga, unke liye Noor ke motiyon ke , yaqoot ke , zamarrud ke, soney ke aur chaandi ke member lagaey jaeyngey, un mein se adnaa darjey ka shakhs, aur un mein se koi bhi adnaa darjey ka nahin hoga, kastoori aur kaafur ke teelon par hoga, aur wo ye mehsus nahin karengey ke kursiyon waley nashist aur barkhaast mein un se afzal hain.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham apney rab ko dekhengey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan , kya tum Suraj dekhney mein aur chaudahwin raat ka chaand dekhney mein shak kartey ho?'' ham ne arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usi tarah tum apney rab ko dekhney mein shak nahin karogey, aur us majlis mein mojud her shakhs se Allah (kisi tarjamaan ke baghair) mukhatib hoga, yahan tak ke wo un mein se eik aadmi se kahega : aey falan bin falan ! kya tujhey falan din yad hai to ne ye aur ye kaha tha, wo duniya mein uski baaz nafarmaniyan aur ehad shikniyaan usey yad karaaeyga to wo arz kerega : rab ji ! kya to ne mujhey bakhsh nahin diya tha? wo farmaeyga , kyon nahin, haan meri maghfirat ki wusat ki badolat hi to apney is maqam ko pahuncha hai, wo usi beech mein hongey to badal ka eik tukda ooper se unhen dhanp lega , wo un par khushgawar barish barsaeyga, aur unhoney us jaisi khushbu kisi chiz mein nahin pai hogi, hamara rab farmaeyga : maine tumhari izzat aur ikram ki khatir jo tayyar kar rakha hai, tum uska qasd (irada) (irada) karo aur (wahan sey) jo tum chaho , wo ley lo , ham eik baazar mein jaeyngey, usey farishton ne gher rakha hoga, is mein aisi aisi chizen hongi jisey aakhon ne dekha hoga na kanon ne suna hoga aur na hi dilon mein uska khayal aaya hoga, ham jo chahengey wo hamarey liye laya jaeyga, wahan kharid aur farokht nahin hogi , aur us baazar mein , jannat waley eik doosrey ko milengey.'' farmaya : ''buland manzilon wala aadmi tawajjoh karega to wo apney se kam tar sey, halanke un mein se koi bhi kam tar nahin, mulaqat karega to wo uskey libas ko dekhega to wo usey tajjub mein dal dega, uski baat khatam nahin hogi yahan tak ke usey khayal aaeyga ke is par jo (libas) hai wo us (libas) se behtar hai, aur ye isliye hai ke kisi ke liye munasib nahin ke wo us (jannat) mein ghamgin ho, phir ham apney gharon ko wapis aaeyngey to hamari azwaj (jodey) (biwiyan) ham se mulaqat kerengi to wo kahengi : khush aamadeed , jab tum hamarey paas se gaey they, to ab jabkey tum hamarey paas aaye ho, us se ziyada khoobsurat ho, ham kahengey : aaj ham ne apney rab jabbaar ki ham nasheenin ikhtiyar ki to ham par lazim tha ke ham usi haalat mein wapis aatey jis haalat mein ham wapis aaye hain.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
5648,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat walon mein se adnaa darjey wala wo hoga jiskey assi hazar khaadim aur bahattar biwiyan hongi , aur uskey jaabiya se san'aa ki darmiyani masafat (doori) jitna, zamarrud, jawaharat aur yaqoot se eik khema nasab (gaada) kiya jaeyga.'' aur isi sanad ke sath hai, farmaya : ''jannat walon mein se (duniya mein) jo koi chhota ya koi bada faut ho jata hai wo sab jannat mein tees baras ke hongey, unki umr us se kabhi ziyada nahin hogi , aur jahannam waley bhi is tarah (tees saal ke) hongey.'' aur isi sanad ke sath farmaya : ''un(jannat walon ke saron) par taaj hongey, unka adnaa sa moti mashriq aur maghrib ke darmiyan ko roshan kar dega.'' aur isi sanad se marwi (bayan) hai, farmaya : ''momin jab jannat mein bachchey ki khahish kerega to uska hamal hona, uski wiladat hona aur uski umr (puri) hona eik ghadi mein ho jaeyga jis tarah wo chaheyga.'' aur Is'haq bin Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ne is hadees (ke bayan) mein farmaya : jab momin jannat mein bachchey ki khahish karega to wo eik ghadi mein ho jaeyga lekin wo uski khahish hi nahin karega.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ''ye hadees gharib hai, Imam ibne-Maja ne chotha fiqra riwayat kiya, jabkey Imam Darmi ne aakhiri. rawahu Tirmizi."
5649,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein hurain ke liye eik ijtima gaah hai jahan wo aawazen buland krengi jo makhluq ne nahin suni hongi , wo kahengi : ham daaimi hain, ham halak nahin hongi , ham to aesh karney waliyan hain, ham mohtaj nahin hongi , aur ham khush rehney waliyan hain, ham naraz nahin hongi , us shakhs ke liye khush khabri ho jo hamarey liye hai aur ham uskey liye hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5650,"Hazrat Haakim bin Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein pani ka darya hai, shehad ka darya hai, doodh ka darya hai, aur sharab ka darya hai, phir (jannat walon ke jannat mein dakhil honey ke) baad nehren niklengi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5651,Aur Imam Darmi ne usey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Darmi.
5652,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi jannat mein, (apni khas) jannat mein karwat badalney se pehley sattar takiyon par tek lagaeyga, phir eik aurat uskey paas aaeygi , aur uskey kandhey ko thapthapaaeygi , wo uskey rukhsaar mein apna chehra dekhega, wo (rukhsaar) aaine se ziyada saaf hoga, aur us (aurat) par adnaa moti mashriq aur maghrib ke darmiyani fasley ko roshan kar dey , wo usko salam karegi to wo usey salam ka jawab dega , aur wo us se puchchhey ga : to kon hai? wo kaheygi : main ''mazeed'' ke zimn se hun, is par sattar libas hongey, uski nazar un (sattar libaason) se guzar jaeygi yahan tak ke unke peechhey uski pindli ka goodaa dekh lega , aur is par eik taaj hoga aur uskey jawahraat mein se adnaa heera mashriq aur maghrib ko roshan kar dey.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5653,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baat kar rahey they, us waqt aap ke paas eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) tha ke jannat walon mein se eik aadmi ne apney rab se kaashtkaari ke mutalliq ijazat talab ki to usney us se farmaya : kya tujhey man pasand chizen muyassar nahin? usney arz kiya, kyon nahin, muyassar hain, lekin main chahta hun ke main kaashtkaari karun, usney beej giraya to pal bhar mein wo ug aaya, barabar ho gaya aur kat bhi gaya, aur wo (ghalley ke dher) pahadon ki tarah they, Allah Taala farmaeyga : ibne-Adam ! isey ley lo , kyonkey koi chiz tera pet nahin bhar sakti .'' us Erabi (dehati) (dehati) ne arz kiya, Allah ki qism ! wo Quraishi ya Ansari hoga kyonkey wo kashtkar hain, aur rahey ham , to ham kashtkar nahin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hans diye. Bukhari."
5654,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kiya, kya jannat waley soeygey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''neend , maut ki behan hai aur jannat waley mareyngey nahin.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5655,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney rab ko saaf zahir taur par dekhogey.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : raawi bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bethey huey they ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaudahwin raat ke chaand ki taraf dekha to farmaya : ''an-qareeb tum apney rab ko isi tarah dekhogey jis tarah tum us chaand ko dekh rahey ho, aur usko dekhney main tum koi tangi mehsus nahin karogey, agar tum uski istataat rakho ke tum tulu aaftaab aur ghurub aaftaab se pehley ki namazon ki adaegi mein maghloob (parajit) na ho jaao to phir unki adaegi zarur karo.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''tulu aaftaab aur uskey ghurub honey se pehley apney rab ki hamd ke sath tasbih bayan karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
5656,"Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab jannat waley jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyngey to Allah Taala farmaeyga : tumhen kisi chiz ki zarurat hai to main tumhen mazeed ata farmaun? wo arz karengey : kya to ne hamarey chehrey safed nahin bana diye? kya to ne hamein jannat mein dakhil nahin farma diya aur to ne hamein jahannam ki aag se nahin bacha liya?'' farmaya : ''hijaab utha liya jaeyga to wo Allah ke chehrey ka deedar karengey, unhen jo kuchh ata kiya gaya un mein se apney rab ka deedar unhen sab se ziyada mehbub hoga.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''un logon ke liye jinhonne achchhey aamaal kiye, achchhaa sawab (jannat) hai aur ziyada (Allah taala ka deedar) hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5657,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat walon mein se sab se adnaa maqam wala wo shakhs hoga jo apney baghaat , apni azwaj (jodey) (biwiyan), apni nematon , apney khaadimon aur apney takhton ko hazar saal ki masafat (doori) tak dekhega (us ki nematoen hazar saal ki masafat (doori) par muheet (rakhi) hongi) aur un mein se Allah ke yahan sab se ziyada moazziz wo hoga jo subah aur Sham uskey chehrey ka deedar karega.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''us roz baaz chehrey tar-o-taza hongey, apney rab ko dekhney waley hongey.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5658,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen Aqeeli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya qiyamat ke roz ham sab Allah ko akeley akeley dekhengey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , kyon nahin.'' maine arz kiya : uski nishani kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu Rizeen ! kya tum sab chaudahwin raat ke chaand ko akeley akeley nahin dekhtey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya, ji haan (dekhtey hain), aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (chaand) to Allah ki makhluq mein se eik makhluq hai, jabkey Allah Taala Ajal aur Aazam hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5659,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha : kya aapney apney rab ko dekha hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(wo) Noor hai, main usey kaisey dekh sakta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
5660,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah Taala ke us farman : ''us (Rasool) ne jo kuchh dekha (aap ke) dil ne is mein dhoka nahin khaya. aur aapney usko eik aur baar bhi dekha.'' ke barey mein farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko apney dil se do martaba dekha. aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney rab ko dekha hai, Ikrima (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kya Allah farmata nahin?'' aankhen uska idraak nahin kar saktin (samajh nahi sakti) jabkey wo aakhon ka idraak kar sakta hai (samajh sakta hai).'' farmaya : tujh par afsos hai ! ye tab hai jab wo apney us Noor ke sath tajalli farmaai jo ke uska Noor hai, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney rab ko do martaba dekha hai. rawahu Muslim aur Tirmizi."
5661,"Hazrat Shobi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Arafat ke maidan mein miley to ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kisi chiz ke mutalliq masla puchha to unhoney (zor sey) Allahu-Akbar kaha yahan tak ke pahadon ne unhen jawab diya, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham bano Hashim hain, Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ne apni rooiyat aur apney kalam ko Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ke darmiyan taqseem farmaya hai, Musa (Alaihissalam) ne do martaba kalam kiya hai jabkey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey do martaba dekha hai. Masruq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya to maine puchha kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney rab ko dekha hai? unhoney farmaya : tum ne aisi chiz ke mutalliq baat ki hai ke merey raungtey khadey ho gaey hain, maine arz ikya : zara sukoon farmaeyn, phir maine ye aayat tilawat ki : ''us (Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ne apney rab ki baaz badi nishaniyan dekhin.'' unhoney farmaya : ye (aayat) tumhen kidhar ley ja rahi hai? us se murad to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) hain, jo shakhs tumhen ye bataey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney rab ko dekha hai? ya jiskey mutalliq aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (bayan karney ka ( hukm diya gaya tha to aapney is mein se koi chiz chupa li? ya aap wo paanch chizen jantey they jinkey mutalliq Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''be-shak qiyamat ka ilm Allah hi ke paas hai, aur wohi barish barsata hai.'' aur ye (ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney rab ko dekha hai) to ye bahut bada jhoot hai, lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko dekha hai aur aapney unhen unki asal surat mein sirf do martaba hi dekha hai, eik martaba sidratul-muntaha ke paas aur eik martaba ajyaad (Makka ke nashebi ilaqey) ke paas , uskey 600 par hain. aur usney ufuq ko bhar diya tha. Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) aur Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuchh izaafey aur kuchh ikhtilaf ke sath riwayat kiya hai, unki riwayat mein hai, Masruq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se arz kiya : Allah Taala ke us farman : ''phir wo qarib hua aur aagey badha, to kamaan ka ya us se bhi kam farq reh gaya.'' ka kya maana hai? unhoney farmaya : wo (Jibrael (Alaihissalam)) aadmi ki surat mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya kartey they, aur is martaba wo apni us surat mein aaye they jo ke unki asal surat hai, to ufuq bhar gaya. (rawahu Tirmizi, اصل الحدیث عند البخاری aur Muslim)."
5662,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah Taala ke farman : ''to kamaan ya us se bhi kam farq reh gaya.'' aur  ''aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo kuch dekha, dil ne is mein dhoka nahin khaya'' aur  ''aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney rab ki badi badi nishaniyan dekhin.'' ke barey mein farmaya : un tamam Suraton mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko dekha hai, unke chhe sau par they. muttafaq aleh. aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : ''aapney jo dekha, dil ne is mein dhoka nahin khaya.'' ke barey mein farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko sabz (hara) jodey mein dekha, usney zamin aur aasman ke darmiyani khala (hissa) ko pur kar rakha tha, aur Tirmizi aur sahih Bukhari ki, Allah Taala ke farman : ''aapney apney rab ki badi badi nishaniyan dekhi .'' riwayat mein hai, farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sabz (hara) libas waley ko dekha usney ufuq bhar diya tha. ( Tirmizi aur qaal : Hasan)."
5663,"Aur Malik bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey, Allah Taala ke us farman : ''wo apney rab ko dekhney waley hongey.'' ke barey mein puchha gaya, isi ke saath unhen bataya gaya ke kuchh log us se ye murad letey hain ke wo rab taala ke sawab ko dekhney waley hongey, Imam Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : unhoney jhoot kaha hai, (agar aisey hai) to phir wo Allah Taala ke us farman : ''hergiz nahin, be-shak wo us roz apney rab ke deedar se rok diye jaeyngey.'' ke barey mein kya kehtey hain? Imam Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : log roze-qiyamat apni aakhon se Allah ka deedar karengey aur farmaya : agar momin qiyamat ke din apney rab ka deedar nahin karengey to phir Allah kafiron ko deedar se mahroomi ki aar (sharm) na dilaataa, farmaya : ''hergiz nahin, be-shak wo (kafir log) us roz apney rab ke deedar se rok diye jaeyngey.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5664,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is beech mein ke jannat waley apni nematon mein mashghool hongey ke achcha unke liye eik Noor chamkeyga , wo apney sar uthaeyngey to achcha unke ooper se rab taala ne un par tajalli farmaee hogi, wo farmaeyga : jannat walo ! Assalamualaikum !'' farmaya : ''ye Allah Taala ka wo farman hai : ''meharban rab ki taraf se salam kaha jaeyga.'' farmaya : ''wo unki taraf dekhega aur wo uski taraf dekhengey, jab tak wo uski taraf dekhtey rahengey wo kisi aur nemat ki taraf tawajjoh nahin karengey yahan tak ke wo un se hijaab kar lega aur uska Noor baqi reh jaeyga.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5665,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhari (ye duniya ki) aag jahannam ki aag ka sattarwaan hissey hai.'' arz kiya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! agar (ye duniya ki aag hi) hoti to wohi kafi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us (jahannam ki aag) ko un (aag ki iqsaam) par unhattar darjey fazilat aur bartari di gaee hai, wo sab us (duniya ki aag) ki haraarat aur tapish ki tarah hai.'' aur alfaz hadees Sahih Bukhari ke hain. aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''tumhari wo aag jo insan jalata hai.'' aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein : (علیھن) aur (کلھن) ke bajaey (علیھا) aur (کلھا) ke alfaz hain. muttafaq aleh."
5666,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam ko laya jaeyga, us roz uski sattar hazar lagaamein hongi aur her lagaam ke sath sattar hazar farishtey hongey jo usey khinch rahey hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
5667,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam walon mein se jis shakhs ko sab se halka azab hoga, wo shakhs wo hoga jiskey jootey aur tasmey aag ke hongey, jin ki wajeh se uska dimagh is tarah kholta hoga jis tarah handiya kholti hai, ''wo ye khayal kerega ke kisi shakhs ko us se ziyada azab nahin ho raha halanke wo sab se halkey azab mein mubtala hoga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5668,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam walon mein se sab se halka azab Abu Talib ko hoga, usney aag ke do jootey pehney hongey, un se uska dimagh kholeyga.'' Bukhari."
5669,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat jahannam walon mein se us shakhs ko laya jaeyga jisey duniya mein sab se ziyada nematen muyassar thin, usey aag main eik ghota diya jaeyga, phir kaha jaeyga : aey insan ! kya tum ne kabhi koi khair aur nemat dekhi thi? kya kisi nemat ka terey paas se kabhi guzar hua tha? wo arz kerega : rab ji ! Allah ki qism ! nahin, (phir) ehale jannat mein se aisey shakhs ko laya jaeyga jisney duniya mein sab se ziyada bad-haali dekhi ho, usey jannat main eik baar ghumaa kar us se puchha jaeyga : aey insan ! kya to ne kabhi koi bad-haali dekhi thi? ya kabhi koi shiddat aur tangi terey paas se guzri thi? wo arz kerega : rab ji ! Allah ki qism ! nahin, na to kabhi bad-haali merey paas se guzri aur na maine kabhi koi shiddat aur tangi dekhi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5670,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Allah , jahannam walon mein se sab se halkay azab mein giraftar shakhs se farmaeyga : agar zamin ki tamam chizen teri milkiyat hon to kya to unhen us (azab ke) badley mein bator fidya dey dega? wo arz kerega : ji haan , wo farmaeyga : maine tujh sey, jabkey to Adam (Alaihissalam) ki pusht mein tha, us se bhi maamuli chiz ka mutalba kya tha ke to merey sath shareek na thehraeyga, lekin to ne inkar kiya, aur merey sath shirk kiya.'' muttafaq aleh."
5671,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kuch aisey log hongey jinhen aag unke takhnon tak pakdeygi , un mein se kisi ke ghutnon tak pahunchi hogi , un mein se kisi ke izaar band tak pahunchi hogi aur un mein se kisi ki gardan ko dabochey huey hogi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5672,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam mein kafir ke do kandhon ke darmiyani fasla tez raftaar sawar ki teen roz ki masafat (doori) jitna hoga.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''kafir ki daadh uhad (pahad) ki jisi hogi , aur uski jild ki motaai teen raat ki masafat (doori) jitni hogi.'' rawahu Muslim. aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''aag ne apney rab se shikayat ki . . . . . .''  (باب تعجیل الصلوات) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
5673,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam ki aag hazar baras jalaai gaee to wo surkh ho gaee , phir usey hazar baras jalaayaa gaya to wo safed ho gaee , phir usey hazar baras jalaayaa gaya to wo siyah ho gaee , wo siyah tareen hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5674,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat kafir ki daadh uhad pahad jaisi hogi , uski raan baizaa (pahad / maqam) ki tarah hogi , aur jahannam mein uskey bethney ki jagah teen raat ki masafat (doori), jaisey (Madine sey) rabza hai, ke barabar hogi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5675,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kafir ki jild ki motaai bayaalees haath hogi , uski daadh uhad pahad ki jaisi hogi aur jahannam mein uskey bethney ki jagah itni hogi jis tarah Makka aur Madina ke darmiyan fasla hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5676,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kafir apni zaban ko farsakh (teen meel) aur do farsakh ghasiteyga aur log usko paaon taley rondengey.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5677,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''al-saood jahannam main eik pahad hai jis par (kafir) ko sattar saal tak musalsal chadhaya jaeyga aur isi tarah (sattar saal tak) usey musalsal giraya jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5678,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (کالمھل) ki tafseer mein farmaya : ''wo til-chhat ki tarah hoga. jab usko uskey chehrey ke qarib kiya jaeyga to uskey chehrey ki jild is mein gir jaeygi.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5679,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kholta hua pani un (jahannam walon) ke saron par dala jaeyga to wo kholta hua pani dakhil ho jaeyga yahan tak ke wo uskey pet ke andar tak pahunch jaeyga aur uskey pet ke andar jo kuchh hai usey kaat dalega yahan tak ke wo uskey qadmon se nikal jaeyga, aur ye wo sahar (gala dena) hai phir usey uski pehli hi haalat par lota diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5680,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah Taala ke farman : ''usey peep pilai jaeygi to wo usey ghoont ghoont piyega.'' farmaya : ''wo uskey munh ke qarib kiya jaeyga to wo usey napasand kerega, jab usey uskey qarib kiya jaeyga to uska chehra jal jaeyga, uskey sar ki jild gir padeygi, jab wo usey piyega to uski antadiyaan kat jaeyngi yahan tak ke wo uski peeth ke raastey bahar nikal aaeyga. Allah Taala farmata hai.'' unhen kholta hua pani pilaya jaeyga to wo unki antadiyaan kaat daleyga.'' aur wo farmata hai : ''aur agar wo fariyad karengey to unki fariyad-rasi aisey pani se ki jaeygi jo til-chhat ki tarah hoga, chehron ko bhoon daleyga, bura peena hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5681,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam ki aag ka chaar deewaron se ehata kiya gaya hai, aur her deewar ki motaai chaalis saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5682,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar (jahannamiyon ke zakhmon ki) peep ka eik dol duniya mein baha diya jaey to duniya waley badboo daar bin jatey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5683,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''Allah se aisey daro jaisey us se darney ka haq hai aur tumhari maut us haal mein aaye ke tum musalman ho.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar zaqqum (thoohar) ka eik qatra duniya mein gira diya jaey to wo zamin walon par unki duniya ki chizon ko kharab kar dey, to us shakhs ki kya haalat hogi jis ka khana hi wohi hoga.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5684,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aur wo us (jahannam) mein is tarah hongey ke unke hont sikud kar ooper chadh gaey hongey aur daant khul gaey hongey.'' farmaya : aag unhen jala deygi to unke ooper waley hont sikud jaeyngey yahan tak ke wo unke sar ke wast (beech) mein pahunch jaeyngiy aur unke nichley hont latak jaeyngey yahan tak ke wo unki naaf tak pahunch jaeyngey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5685,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logo ! (apney gunahon par dartey huey) roya karo, agar tum (roney ki) istataat na rakho to phir apney aap ko roney par aamada karo, kyonkey jahannam waley jahannam mein ro'eyn gey yahan tak ke unke aansu unke chehron par is tarah rawan hongey jaisey wo behti naaliyaan hain, aur phir rotey rotey unke aansu khatam ho jaeyngey to phir khoon behnaa shuru ho jaeyga, aankhen zakhmi ho jaeyngi (aur is qadr aansu aur khoon baheyga ke) agar is mein kashtiyan chhod di jaeyn to wo chalna shuru kar den.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
5686,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam walon par bhook dal di jaeygi, aur wo (bhook ki takleef) us azab (ki takleef) ke barabar hogi jis mein wo mubtala hongey, wo fariyad karengey to unki fariyad-rasi kaantay daar khaney ke zariey ki jaeygi, wo mota karega na bhook mitaeyga , wo khaney ki fariyad karengey to unki is tarah ke khaney se fariyad rasi ki jaeygi jo halaq mein atak janey wala hoga, wo yad karengey ke wo duniya mein , halaq mein atak janey wali chizon ko guzarney ke liye pani piya kartey they, wo pani ke liye fariyad karengey to lohey ke aankdon ke zariey garm kholta hua pani unke qarib kiya jaeyga, jab wo unke chehron ke qarib hoga to wo unke chehron ko jala dega , aur unke pet mein dakhil hoga to wo pet mein mojud her chiz ko kaat daleyga , wo kahengey : jahannam ke darbaanon ko bulaao, to wo jawab dengey, kya tumharey Rasool mojzat lekar tumharey paas nahin aaye they? wo kahengey : kyon nahin, aaye they, wo kahengey : (phir) pukartey raho, aur kafiron ki pukar khasarey mein hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (kafir) kahengey : Maalik ko bulaao, wo kahengey, Maalik ! tera rab hamein maut hi dey dey.'' farmaya : ''wo unhen jawab dega : be-shak tum hamesha hamesha azab mein theherney waley ho.'' Aamash (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : mujhey bataya gaya ke unki dua aur Maalik ke unhen jawab deney mein hazar saal ka waqfa hoga. farmaya : ''wo kahengey , apney rab se dua karo, tumharey rab se behtar koi nahin, wo arz karengey : hamarey parwardigar ! hamari shaqaawat (sakhti) ham par ghalib aa gaee aur ham gumrah log they, hamarey parwardigar ! hamein yahan se nikal dey , agar ham ne dobara wohi kaam kiye (jin par to naraz hota hai) to ham zalim hongey.'' farmaya : ''wo unhen jawab dega : zaleel ho kar isi mein raho , aur mujh se kalam na karo.'' farmaya : ''us waqt wo her qism ki khair aur bhalai se mayus ho jaeyngey, aur us waqt wo cheekh aur pukar , hasrat aur tabahi mein mubtala ho jaeyngey.'' aur Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) (raawi) bayan kartey hain, log is hadees ko marfoo bayan nahin kartey. rawahu Tirmizi."
5687,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mainne Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''maine tumhen jahannam ki aag se aagah kar diya, maine tumhen jahannam ki aag se aagah aur khabrdar kar diya.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bar-bar ye farmatey rahey, yahan tak ke agar aap meri us jagah hotey to baazar waley usey sun letey , aur yahan tak ke aap (ke kandhey) par jo chadar thi wo aap ke qadmon par gir padi. rawahu Darmi."
5688,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar itna seesa.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne piyaley ki taraf ishara kartey huey farmaya : ''aasman se zamin ki taraf chhoda jaey aur wo paanch sau meel ki masafat (doori) hai, to wo Sham se pehley zamin par pahunch jaey, aur agar usey zanjeer ke sirey se chhoda jaey to usey uski asal (pehli kadi) tak ya uski gehraai tak pahunchney ke liye mutawatir (lagatar) chaalis saal lagengey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
5689,"Hazrat abu burda (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam main eik wadi hai jisey ( ھَبْھَبْ ( kaha jata hai, is mein her qism ke sarkash aur baaghi rahengey.'' rawahu Darmi."
5690,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam walon ke jism , jahannam mein badey ho jaeyngey yahan tak ke unki kaan ki lo se kandhey tak saat so saal ki masafat (doori) hogi , uski jild ki motaai sattar haath hogi aur uski daadh uhad pahad jaisi hogi.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5691,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Haris bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam mein bakhti oonton ki tarah azdahe hai, un mein se eik daseyga to wo chaalis saal tak uskey zahar ka asar mehsus karta rahega, is mein paalaan bandhoon khachcharon ki tarah ke bichchhu hongey, un mein se koi daseyga to wo shakhs chaalis saal tak uske zahar ka asar mehsus karta rahega.'' dono hadison ko Imam Ahmed ne riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed."
5692,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees bayan ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Suraj aur Chaand ko lapet kar jahannam mein phenk diya jaeyga.'' is par Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : unka kya gunah hai? unhoney farmaya : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees bayan kar raha hun, tab Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh ho gaey. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi al-ba's aur Nushur)."
5693,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sirf bad-naseeb shakhs hi jahannam mein jaeyga.''arz kiya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! bad-naseeb shakhs kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney Allah ki khatir koi nek kaam na kiya aur na uski khatir koi gunah chhoda.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5694,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat aur jahannam ne behes aur mubaahasa (debate) kiya to jahannam ne kaha : mujhey takabbur karney walon aur sarkashon ke liye khas kar diya gaya hai, jannat ne kaha, meri to haalat ye hai ke mujh mein (ziyada tar) sirf zaeef aur kam rutba waley aur duniya se bezar log hongey, Allah ne jannat se farmaya : to meri rehmat hai, main terey zariey apney bandon mein se jis par chahun ga rehem farmaunga, aur jahannam se farmaya : to mera azab hai, main terey zariey apney bandon mein se jisey chahunga azab dunga, aur tum dono bhar jaaogi, rahi jahannam to wo nahin bhareygi yahan tak ke Allah is mein apna qadam rakhega to wo kaheygi : bas, bas, bas tab wo bhareygi aur uska baaz hissa, baaz ke sath mil jaeyga, aur Allah apni makhluq mein se kisi par zulm nahin kerega, rahi jannat to Allah uskey liye eik makhluq paida farmaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
5695,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam mein logon ko dala jaeyga to wo kehti rahegi : kuchh aur bhi hai? yahan tak ke Rabul-Izzat is mein apna qadam rakhega to uska baaz hissey baaz ke sath mil jaeyga aur wo kaheygi : teri izzat aur karam ki qism ! bas, bas ! aur jannat mein mazeed gunjaaish hogi yahan tak ke Allah uskey liye eik makhluq paida farmaeyga, aur unhen jannat ke zayed hissey mein basaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (حفت الجنۃ بالمکارہ) kitab الرقاق mein zikr ki gaee hai."
5696,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne jannat ko paida farmaya to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) se farmaya : jaao usey dekho, wo gaey aur unhoney usko aur uskey rehney walon ke liye Allah ne jo kuchh tayyar kar rakha tha usko dekha, phir wapis aaye to arz kiya : rab ji ! teri izzat ki qism ! uskey mutalliq jo bhi suneyga wo is mein dakhil hoga, phir Allah Taala ne uskey gird nagawar chizon ki baad laga di, phir farmaya : Jibrael ! jaao aur usey dekho.'' farmaya : ''wo gaey aur usey dekha, phir aaye aur arz kiya : rab ji ! teri izzat ki qism ! mujhey andesha hai ke is mein koi eik bhi dakhil nahin hoga.'' farmaya : ''jab Allah ne jahannam ko paida farmaya to farmaya : Jibrael ! jaao aur usey dekho.'' farmaya : ''wo gaey aur usey dekha, phir aaye aur arz kiya, rab ji ! teri izzat ki qism ! uskey mutalliq jo suneyga wo is mein dakhil nahin hoga.'' Allah Taala ne uskey gird shehwaat ki baad laga di, phir farmaya : ''Jibrael ! jaao aur usey dekho.'' farmaya : ''wo gaey aur usey dekha to (aa kar) arz kiya : rab ji ! teri izzat ki qism ! mujhey andesha hai ke is mein dakhil honey se koi bhi nahin bacheyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
5697,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz hamein Namaz padhaai , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par chadhey aur apney haath se masjid ke qibley ki taraf ishara kiya, phir farmaya : ''ab jabke main tumhen Namaz padha raha tha to mujhey us deewar ki taraf jannat aur jahannam ke manazir dikhai diye , maine aaj ke din ki tarah na to koi bhali chiz dekhi aur na aisi koi buri chiz dekhi.'' Bukhari."
5698,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke bano Tameem (qabiley) ke kuchh log aap ke paas aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banu Tameem ! tum khushkhabri qubul karo.'' unhoney arz kiya, aapney hamein khushkhabri to sunadi, aap hamein ata bhi farmaeyn, itney mein ehale Yamen se kuchh log aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Yamen walo ! tum khushkhabri qubul karo, jabkey bano Tameem ne usey qubul nahin kiya.'' unhoney arz kiya, ham ne qubul kiya, aur ham aap ki khidmat mein isliye hazir huey hain ta ke ham Deen mein samajh boojh hasil karen aur sab se pehley kya chiz thi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tha, aur us se pehley koi chiz nahin thi, aur uska arsh pani par tha, phir usney aasman aur zamin paida farmaai , aur zikr (loh (takhti) mehfooz) mein her chiz likhi.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir eik aadmi merey paas aaya to usney kaha : Imran ! apni oontni ki khabar lo, wo ja chuki hai, main usey talash karney chala gaya, Allah ki qism ! maine khahish ki ke wo chali jati aur main (wahan sey) na uthta. Bukhari."
5699,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik jagah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein taweel (lamba) khutba irshad farmaya , aapney hamein makhluq ki ibtida (shuruat) se batana shuru kiya (aur batatey gaey) yahan tak ke jannat waley apni manaazil mein aur jahannam waley apni jagahon mein dakhil ho gaey. aur jisney usey yad rakhna tha usney usey yad rakha , aur jisey bhoolna tha wo bhool gaya. Bukhari."
5700,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah taala ne makhluq ki takhleeq (banane) se pehley eik maktoob (loh (takhti) mehfooz) tehreer kiya ke meri rehmat , merey ghazab par ghalib hai aur wo arsh ke ooper uskey paas likha hua hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
5701,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''farishtey Noor se paida kiye gaey, jin dhuein aur sholay wali aag se paida kiye gaey jabkey Adam (Alaihissalam) us chiz se paida kiye gaey jo tumhen bayan kar di gaee hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5702,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ka Khaaka banaya to Allah ne jis qadr chaha ke wo unhen jannat mein chhod dey to usney isey is qadr jannat mein chhod diya, Iblees unke gird chakkar laganey laga ta ke wo dekhey ke wo kya chiz hai? jab usney unhen (andar sey) khaali dekha to usney pehchan liya ke ye aisi makhluq ki takhleeq ki gaee hai, jo (apney nafs ki khaahishat par) qabu nahin rakh sakeygi.'' rawahu Muslim."
5703,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne assi saal ki umr mein taisey ke sath khatna kiya.'' muttafaq aleh."
5704,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ne sirf teen jhoot boley , is mein se do Allah ki khatir they, unhoney kaha : ''main bimar hun.'' aur ye kehna : ''balke ye unke badey ne kiya hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik roz wo (Ibrahim (Alaihissalam)) aur (unki ehliya) saara eik zalim badshah ki saltanat se guzar rahey they to us (badshah) ko bataya gaya ke yahan eik aadmi hai aur uskey sath eik intehai khoobsurat aurat hai, us (badshah) ne Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko bula bheja aur un se Saara ke mutalliq puchha ke ye kon hai? unhoney kaha : meri behan hai, phir Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) Saara ke paas aaye aur unhen bataya ke zalim badshah hai agar usey pata chal jaey ke to meri ehliya (biwi) hai to wo terey barey mein mujh par ghalib aa jaeyga, agar wo tujh se puchhey to yehi kehna ke to meri behan hai, kyonkey to meri Islaami behan hai, roey zamin par merey aur terey siwa koi aur momin nahin, us (badshah) ne saara (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja, unhen laya gaya to Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) Namaz padhney lagey jab wo unke paas gaeen aur usney dast darazi (hath badhane) ki koshish ki to usey pakad liya gaya.'' aur is tarah bhi marwi (bayan) hai ke ''uska gala ghoont diya gaya yahan tak ke usney zamin par apna paaon maara aur kaha : Allah se merey liye dua karo main tumhen nuqsan nahin pahunchaunga, unhoney Allah se dua ki to usey chhod diya gaya, usney dusri martaba dast darazi (hath badhane) ki koshish ki to usey isi tarah ya us se bhi sakhti ke sath pakad liya gaya, usney kaha : Allah se merey liye dua karo, main tumhen nuqsan nahin pahunchaunga, unhoney Allah se dua ki to usey chhod diya gaya, usney apney kisi darbaan ko bulaya aur kaha : tune merey paas kisi insan ko nahin balke kisi shetan ko bheja hai, usney Saara ki khidmat ke liye unhen Haajir ata ki, wo Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke paas aayin to wo khadey Namaz ada kar rahey they, unhoney apney haath ke isharay se puchha : kya hua? unhoney bataya : Allah ne kafir ki tadbeer ko usi par ulat diya hai, aur usney khidmat ke liye Haajir di hai.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ''ehale Arab (barish par guzaara karney walo) ye Haajir tumhari walida hain. muttafaq aleh."
5705,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke muqabley mein shak karney ka ziyada haq rakhtey hain, jab unhoney kaha : ''rab ji ! mujhey dikha ke to mardon ko kis tarah zinda kerega.'' Allah Loot (Alaihissalam) par rehem farmaai wo zabardast saharey (yani Allah Taalaa) ki panah letey they, aur agar main itni muddat tak, jitni muddat tak Yusuf (Alaihissalam) qaid khaney mein rahey, qaid khaney mein rehta to main bulaney waley ki baat zarur maan leta.'' muttafaq aleh."
5706,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Musa (Alaihissalam) badey hi sharam w haya waley insan they, unke haya ki wajeh se unki jild se kuchh bhi nahin dekha ja sakta tha, Bani-Israel ke jin logon ne aap (Alaihissalam) ko aziyat pahunchaai thi wo pahuncha kar rahey, unhoney kaha : ye apni kisi jildi bimari ki wajeh se is qadr apna badan chupa kar rakhtey hain, ye ya to baras ke mareez hain ya unke khasiye (fotey) phool gaey hain, Allah ne irada farmaya ke wo unko kamiyon se be-aeb Sabit karey, eik roz wo akeley ghusl karney ke liye aaye to apney kapdey utaar kar eik patthar par rakh diye , aur wo patthar unke kapdey lekar bhag gaya, Musa (Alaihissalam) bhi tezi ke sath uskey peechhey bhagney lagey aur kehney lagey : patthar ! merey kapdey (wapis kar do main aur kuchh nahin chahta) wo (us tarah kehtey huey) Bani-Israel ki eik jamaat tak pahunch gaey, unhoney unko uriyaan (nangi) haalat mein dekh liya ke Allah ne jo takhleeq farmaai hai wo ahsan hai, aur unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! Musa (Alaihissalam) mein koi naqs nahin, aur unhoney apney kapdey liye aur pathar ko maarney lagey , Allah ki qism ! unki maar ke , teen , chaar ya paanch nishan pathar par pad gaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5707,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ayub (Alaihissalam) uriyaan (nangi) haalat mein ghusl kar rahey they ke un par soney ki tiddiyan girin to Ayub (Alaihissalam) unhen kapdey mein jama karney lagey to unke rab ne unhen aawaz di, Ayub ! kya maine tujhey maal ata karkey in (tiddiyon) se be-niyaz nahin kar diya? unhoney arz kiya, teri izzat ki qism ! kyon nahin, lekin main teri barkat se kaisey be-niyaz reh sakta hun.'' Bukhari."
5708,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, do aadmiyon ne aapas mein bura bhala kaha, un mein se eik musalman tha aur eik Yahudi tha, musalman ne kaha, us zaat ki qism jisney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tamam jahan walon par fazilat ata farmaai ! Yahudi ne kaha is zaat ki qism jisney Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam jahan walon par fazilat ata farmaee , musalman ne us waqt apna haath uthaya aur Yahudi ke chehrey par thappad raseed kar diya? Yahudi , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur apna aur musalman ka maamla aap ko bataya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey Musa (Alaihissalam) par foqiyat na do , kyonkey roze-qiyamat log be-hosh ho jaeyngey to main bhi unke sath be-hosh ho jaaunga, aur mujhey sab se pehley hosh aaeyga to main dekhunga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ke eik koney ko thaamey huey hongey, main nahin janta ke wo be-hosh honey walon mein se they aur mujh se pehley hosh mein aagey ya wo un mein se they jinhen Allah ne us (be-hoshi) se mustashnaa (apwaad) qarar dey diya.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''main nahin janta ke wo taur ke roz jo be-hosh huey they wohi unke liye kafi tha, ya wo mujh se pehley uthaey gaey, aur main nahin kehta ke koi Yunus bin Matti (Alaihissalam) se afzal hai.'' Bukhari."
5709,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''Anbiya ko eik doosrey par bartari na do.'' aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''Anbiya ko eik doosrey par fazilat na do.'' muttafaq aleh."
5710,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi bandey ke liye munasib nahin ke wo kahey ke main Yunus bin Matti se behtar hun.'' aur Sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jisney kaha ke main Yunus bin Matti se behtar hun to usney jhoot kaha.'' muttafaq aleh."
5711,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo ghulam jisey khizr (Alaihissalam) ne qatl kya tha wo kafir paida hua tha, agar wo zinda rehta to wo apney waliden ko sarkashi aur kufr par majbur karta.'' muttafaq aleh."
5712,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khizr (Alaihissalam) ka naam khizr isliye rakha gaya ke wo eik khushk zamin par bethey they, to wo (zameen) unke baad sarsabz ho kar lahlahaaney lagi.'' Bukhari."
5713,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maut ka farishta Musa bin Imran (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to usney unhen kaha : apney rab ka hukm qubul karo (main aap ki rooh qabz karney aaya hun).'' farmaya : ''Musa (Alaihissalam) ne maut ke farishtey ki aankh par thappad maara aur usey phod diya.'' farmaya : ''wo farishta Allah ke paas wapis chala gaya aur arz kiya, to ne mujhey apney eik aisey bandey ki taraf bheja jo marna nahin chahta , aur usney meri aankh bhi phod di hai, farmaya : Allah ne uski aankh usey lota di, aur farmaya : merey bandey ke paas dobara jaao , aur usey kaho : tum zindagi chahtey ho, agar tum zindagi chahtey ho to apna haath bail ki kamar par rakho aur jitney baal tumharey haath ke nichey aa jaeyngey tum itney saal zinda rahogey, farmaya : ''phir kya hoga? farmaya : phir tum mar jaaogey, farmaya : phir ab isi haalat mein rooh qabz kar lo , aur arz kiya : rab ji ! mujhey arz muqaddas (Baitul-Maqdis) ke itna qarib kar dey ke agar koi pathar phainkney wala phenkey to wo wahan (Baitul-Maqdis) tak pahunch sakey.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! agar main us (Baitul-Maqdis) ke paas hota to main surkh tiley ke paas , raastey ke eik janib , tumhen unki qabr dikhata.'' muttafaq aleh."
5714,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey Anbiya (Alaihissalam) dikhaye gaey, Musa (Alaihissalam) dubley patley hain, goya wo Shanuaa qabiley ke mardon jaisey hain, maine Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) ko dekha, aur maine jinhen dekha un mein se wo Urwa bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se ziyada mushaabihat rakhtey they, maine Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko dekha wo sab se ziyada , tumharey sathi , yani Muhammad se mushaabihat rakhtey hain, aur maine Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ko dekha to wo un logon mein se jinhen maine dekha hai Dahiya bin Khalifa se sab se ziyada mushaabihat rakhtey hain.'' rawahu Muslim. ya Bukhari."
5715,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Mairaj ki raat maine Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekha, aap ka rang gandumi, daraz qad aur baal ghoongariyaaley they, goya wo Shanuaa qabiley ke afrad mein se hon, aur maine Esa (Alaihissalam) ko dekha, unka qad darmiyana , rang surkhi maael safed tha aur baal ghungariyaaley nahin balke sidhey they, maine jahannam ke darogha Maalik aur Dajjaal ko bhi dekha, ye un nishaniyon mein se thin jo Allah ne mujhey dikhayen thin, aap un (Musa (Alaihissalam)) se mulaqat karney mein kisi qism ke shak mein mubtala na hon.'' muttafaq aleh."
5716,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Mairaj ki raat meri Musa (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui.'' aapney unka wasf (khubi) bayan kiya ke '' wo eik dubley patley sidhey baalon waley aadmi hain, goya wo Shanuaa qabiley ke aadmi hain, maine Esa (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat ki, unka qad darmiyana aur rang surkh tha, goya wo ghusl khaney se nikley hain, maine Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat ki, unki aulad mein se main unke ziyada mushabeh hun.'' farmaya : ''merey paas do bartan laye gaey, un mein se eik mein doodh aur doosrey mein sharab thi, mujhey kaha gaya : dono mein se jo chaho pasand kar lo, maine doodh liya aur usey pi liya, mujhey kaha gaya, aap ko fitrat ki rehnumai ki gaee , agar aap sharab letey to aap ki ummat gumrah ho jati.'' muttafaq aleh."
5717,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath makkey aur Madiney ke darmiyan safar kiya, ham eik wadi se guzrey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon si wadi hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, wadi azraq hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''goya main Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekh raha hun.'' aapney unke rang aur unke baalon ke mutalliq kuchh bataya, aur bataya ke'' wo apni dono ungliyan apney kanon mein rakhey huey they, wo talbiya ke zariey Allah se darte hue us wadi se guzar rahey hain.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir ham ne safar kiya aur ham ghaati par pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon si ghaati hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, harshi ya lift. farmaya : ''goya main Yunus (Alaihissalam) ko surkh oontni par Sawar dekh raha hun, unhoney ooni jubba pehna hua hai, aur unki oontni ki nakel khajoor ki shaakhon se bani hui hai, aur wo bhi talbiya kehtey huey us wadi se guzar rahey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
5718,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Dawud (Alaihissalam) par Zabur ki qirat aasan kar di gaee thi, wo apni sawaariyon par zeen kasney ka hukm farmatey aur wo sawaariyon par zeen kasey janey se pehley hi us (zaboor) ki qirat mukammal kar letey they, aur wo sirf apney haathon ki kamai khatey they.'' Bukhari."
5719,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do aurten thin unke sath unke bete bhi they, bhediya aaya aur wo un mein se eik ke bete ko ley gaya, eik ne apni sath wali se kaha : wo to terey bete ko lekar gaya hai, aur dusri ne kaha : (nahin) wo terey bete ko lekar gaya hai, chunanche wo dono Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke paas muqadma ley gaeen to unhoney badi ke haq mein faisla kar diya, phir wo dono Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzrin aur unhoney pura waqia bayan kiya to unhoney farmaya : mujhey chhuri do main usey tukdey karkey tum dono ke darmiyan taqseem kar deta hun, chhoti ne kaha : Allah aap par rehem farmaai , aisey na karen wo usi ka beta hai, unhoney uskey mutalliq chhoti ke haq mein faisla kar diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
5720,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Suleman (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : aaj raat main apni nawwey begamaat (biwiyon) aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai, so begamaat ke paas jaaunga , wo sab Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ghud sawar bachhon ko janm dengi. farishtey ne unhen kaha : Insha- Allah (agar Allah ne chaha) kaho, unhoney na kaha aur (ye kehna) bhool gaey, wo unke paas gaey (unke sath jima (sambhog) kiya) aur un mein se sirf eik hamila hui, aur usney bhi naqis bachchey ko janm diya, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar wo Insha-Allah keh detey to wo sarey Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ghud sawar hotey.'' muttafaq aleh."
5721,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Zakariya (Alaihissalam) badhai they.'' rawahu Muslim.
5722,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) se duniya aur aakhirat mein aur logon ki nisbat ziyada qurbat daar hun, Anbiya (Alaihissalam) allaati (eik baap ki aulad) bhai hain, unki maaeyn alag-alag hain, jabkey unka Deen eik hai, aur hamarey (merey aur Esa (Alaihissalam)) ke darmiyan koi Nabi nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
5723,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Esa bin Maryam (Alaihissalam) ke ilawa , shetan her nau-maulood (nawjaat) ko uski paidaish ke waqt apni do ungliyon se uskey pehlu mein kachokey lagata hai. wo unhen bhi kachokey laganey gaya tha, lekin usney hijaab mein kachokey laga diye.'' muttafaq aleh."
5724,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''murdon mein se to bahut se kamil huey lekin aurton mein se Maryam binte Imran aur Aasiya zauja Firon kamaal ko pahunchin, aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko tamam aurton par aisey hi bartari hasil hai jaisey sareed ko tamam khaanon par fazilat hasil hai.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : (ya khair al-bariya), Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : (أی الناس اکرم) aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ((الکریم ابن الکریم) باب المفاخرۃ و العصبیۃ) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
5725,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! jab rab-taalaa ne apni makhluq ko paida farmaya to us se pehley wo kahan tha? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abr (badal) mein , uskey nichey hawa thi aur uskey ooper hawa thi, aur usney apna arsh pani par takhleeq farmaya.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : Yazid bin Harun ne kaha : عماء se murad hai uskey sath koi chiz nahin thi. rawahu Tirmizi."
5726,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney naqal kiya ke wo Bat'haa main eik jamaat ke sath bethey huey they, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un mein tashrif farma they, itney mein badal ka eik tukda guzra to unhoney uski taraf dekha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum usey kya naam detey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya : ''السحاب'', farmaya : ''المزن'', unhoney arz kiya : ''المزن'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''العنان'' unhoney arz kiya : ''العنان'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke aasman aur zamin ke darmiyan kitni masafat (doori) hai? '' unhoney arz kiya : ham nahin jantey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un dono ke darmiyan ya to ikhattar ya behataar ya tehattar saal ki masafat (doori) hai, aur aasman jo uskey ooper hai isi tarah hai.'' yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saton aasman giney.'' phir saatwen aasman ke ooper eik samandar hai, ooper waley aur nichley hissey ke darmiyan itni hi masafat (doori) hai, jaisey aasman se doosrey aasman tak , phir uskey ooper aath farishtey hain jo pahadi bakron ki shakal ke hain, unke khuron aur peeth ke darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna aasman se aasman tak hai, phir unki pushton par arsh hai, uskey nichley aur ooper waley hissey ke darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna aasman se doosrey aasman ke darmiyan fasla hai. phir uskey ooper Allah hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
5727,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to usney arz kiya janen mashaqqat mein pad gaeen , baal bachchey bhook ka shikar ho gaey, amwaal khatam ho gaey aur janwer halak ho gaey, aap Allah se hamarey liye barish ki dua farmaeyn, ham aap ke zariey Allah se sifarish kartey hain aur Allah ke zariey aap se sifarish kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Subhanallah ! Subhanallah !'' aap musalsal tasbih bayan kartey rahey yahan tak ke ye chiz aap ke Sahaba ke chehron se malum honey lagi , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujh par afsos hai, kisi par Allah ko sifarishi nahin banaya jata, Allah ki shaan is se azeem tar hai, tujh par afsos hai, kya tum jantey ho, Allah (ki azmat aur kibriyaai) kya hai? be-shak uska arsh uskey aasmano par is tarah hai.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni ungliyon se ishara farmaya jaisey is par quba ho.'' wo us wajeh se is tarah aawaz nikalta hai jis tarah sawar ki wajeh se paalaan aawaz nikalta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5728,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey ijazat di gaee ke main Allah ke farishton mein se eik farishtey ka zikr karun jo haameleene-arsh mein se hai, uskey kanon ki lo aur uskey kandhon ke darmiyan saat sau saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
5729,"Hazrat Zarara bin Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Jibrael (Alaihissalam) se puchha : ''kya tum ne apney rab ko dekha hai? ''(us sawal sey) Jibrael (Alaihissalam) laraz gaey aur farmaya : Muhammad ! merey aur uskey darmiyan Noor ke sattar pardey hain, agar main un mein se kisi ke qarib chala jaaun to main jal jaaun.'' Al-Masabeh mein is tarah hai. (rawahu fi Masaabeh al Sunnah)."
5730,"Hazrat Abu Nuaim ne usey huliya mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, albatta unhoney zikr nahin kiya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) laraz gaey.'' (rawahu Abu Nuaim fi huliya al-auliyaa)."
5731,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Israafeel (Alaihissalam) ko paida farmaya , usney jis roz se usey paida farmaya wo us waqt se apney qadmon par khada hai aur wo apni nazar tak nahin uthata , uskey aur uskey Rab Tabarak w taala ke darmiyan sattar Noor hain, jo us Noor ke qarib jata hai to wo jal jata hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney usey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
5732,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah Taala ne Adam (Alaihissalam) aur uski aulad ko paida farmaya to farishton ne arz kiya, rab ji ! tune unhen paida farmaya hai, wo khatey peetey, shadiyaan kartey aur sawari kartey hain, aur to unke liye duniya muqarrar kar dey aur hamarey liye aakhirat muqarrar farma dey, Allah Taala ne farmaya : main us (makhluq) ko, jisey maine apney haathon se takhleeq kiya aur us main apni rooh phunki, usey main us makhluq ke barabar nahin karunga jisey maine kaha bin ja aur wo bin gaee.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
5733,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin Allah ke yahan baaz farishton se bhi ziyada moazziz hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
5734,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mera haath pakad kar farmaya : ''Allah ne mitti (zameen) ko haftey ke din paida farmaya, itwaar ke roz is mein pahad paida farmaai , peer ke din darkht paida farmaey, makruh chizen mangal ke din paida farmaeen, buddh ke roz Noor paida farmaya , Jumerat ke roz is mein chopaey phelaey aur Adam (Alaihissalam) ko Juma ke din Asr ke baad makhluq mein sab se aakhir par paida farmaya, aur din ki aakhiri ghadi Asr aur Sham ke darmiyan hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
5735,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, is beech mein ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba bethey huey they ke eik badal aaya to Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke ye kya hai? '' unhoney arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye عنان hai, ye zamin ko sairab karney wala hai, Allah isko us qom ki taraf haank kar ley jata hai jo na to uska shukr ada kartey hain aur na us se dua kartey hain.'' phir farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho tumharey ooper kya hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' رقیع (aasman ka naam) eik mehfooz chhat aur thami hui moaj hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke tumharey aur uskey darmiyan kitna fasla hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, farmaya : ''tumharey aur uskey darmiyan paanch so saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' phir farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke uskey ooper kya hai? '' unhoney arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, farmaya : ''aasman aur un dono ke darmiyan paanch sau saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' raawi bayan karta hai ke phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isi tarah farmaya yahan tak ke aapney saat aasman giney.'' aur her do aasman ke darmiyan itni hi masafat (doori) hai jitni aasman aur zamin ke darmiyan hai.'' phir farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho uskey ooper kya hai?'' unhoney arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey ooper arsh hai, uskey aur aasman ke darmiyan itni hi masafat (doori) hai jitni do aasmano ke darmiyan hai.'' phir farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke tumharey nichey kya hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, farmaya : ''wo zamin hai.'' phir farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho uskey nichey kya hai?'' unhoney arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, farmaya : ''uskey nichey eik dusri zamin hai, un dono ke darmiyan paanch so saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne saat zameenein shumar kin.'' aur her do zaminon ke darmiyan paanch sau saal ki masafat (doori) hai.'' phir farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! agar tum nichli zamin ki taraf rassi latkaao to wo Allah ke ilm mein hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat ki : ''wohi awwal , wohi aakhir , wohi zahir , wohi baatin hai aur wo her chiz ka ilm rakhta hai.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat aayat is par dalalat karti hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne irada farmaya ke wo Allah ke ilm , uski qudrat aur uski badshahat mein girti hai, aur Allah ka ilm aur qudrat aur uski badshahat her jagah par hai jabkey wo arsh par  (mustawi) hai, jaisa ke usney apney mutalliq apni kitab mein bayan farmaya hai. rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
5736,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Adam (Alaihissalam) ka lambaee saath (60) haath aur arz (chaudaee) saat (7) haath tha.'' rawahu Ahmed.
5737,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! sab se pehley Nabi kon they? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Adam (Alaihissalam).'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya wo Nabi they? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, aisey Nabi they jin par saheefa nazil kiya gaya tha.'' maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Rasool kitney they? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''300 aur 10 se kuchh ooper ki bheed thi.'' aur Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai, Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ki kul tadaad kitni hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik lakh chobis hazar, un mein se Rasulon ki tadaad 315 eik bheed hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
5738,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabar , mushahidey ki tarah nahin hoti , kyonkey Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko unki qom ke bachdey ko mabud bananey ke mutalliq bataya to unhoney الواح (takhtiyan) nahin phenkin, jab unhoney apni aakhon se dekh liya jo unhoney kiya tha, to unhoney takhtiyan phenk Deen aur wo toot gaeen.'' teeno (balke chaaron) hadison ko Imam Ahmed (Raziallahu anhu) ne naqal kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed."
